%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cow%20Vigilante's%20Video%2C%20Police%20Moves%20In%20Focus%20After%20Haryana%20Violence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20deaths%20of%20at%20least%20six%20people%2C%20including%20two%20police%20personnel%2C%20in%20clashes%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20that%20erupted%20on%20Monday%20around%2050%20km%20south%20of%20New%20Delhi%2C%20and%20simmered%20even%20a%20day%20later%2C%20have%20brought%20questions%20about%20the%20role%20of%20social%20media%20posts%20and%20alleged%20inaction%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20authorities%20in%20sharp%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20began%20after%20a%20Hindu%20religious%20procession%20passed%20through%20the%20Muslim-dominated%20Nuh%20district%20in%20Haryana%20state.%20While%20the%20situation%20remains%20tense%2C%20questions%20are%20being%20raised%20over%20the%20police's%20inaction%2C%20specifically%20regarding%20their%20failure%20to%20address%20the%20brewing%20tension%20on%20social%20media%2C%20the%20continued%20absence%20of%20an%20arrest%2C%20and%20their%20inability%20to%20anticipate%20communal%20unrest%20in%20a%20sensitive%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clashes%20have%20been%20blamed%2C%20in%20part%2C%20on%20a%20video%20posted%20on%20social%20media%20by%20Monu%20Manesar%2C%20a%20self-proclaimed%20'%3Cem%3Egau%20rakshak%3C%2Fem%3E'%20or%20cow%20vigilante%20accused%20of%20the%20murder%20of%20two%20Muslim%20cattle%20traders%20last%20year.%20Manesar's%20video%2C%20in%20which%20he%20declared%20his%20intention%20to%20participate%20in%20a%20religious%20event%20and%20urged%20others%20to%20join%20him%2C%20provoked%20a%20strong%20reaction%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20with%20some%20members%20challenging%20and%20threatening%20Manesar%20in%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20Manesar%20ultimately%20not%20attending%20the%20event%2C%20his%20post%20alone%20was%20enough%20to%20ignite%20tensions%20in%20the%20region.%20Chaudhary%20Aftab%20Ahmed%2C%20the%20MLA%20from%20Nuh%2C%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20believe%20that%20it%20is%20a%20failure%20of%20the%20administration.%20Before%20the%20atmosphere%20got%20tense%2C%20we%20went%20to%20the%20authorities%20and%20told%20them%20they%20should%20take%20steps%20before%20it%20escalated.%20If%20the%20right%20steps%20were%20taken%20at%20the%20appropriate%20time%2C%20this%20would%20not%20have%20happened.%20The%20rumour%20that%20Monu%20Manesar%20is%20here%20also%20added%20to%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20government%20officials%20in%20both%20Nuh%20and%20Gurugram%20met%20with%20representatives%20of%20the%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%20communities%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20appealing%20for%20calm.%20But%20Gurugram%20continued%20to%20experience%20unrest%20as%20mobs%20roamed%20the%20streets%2C%20setting%20fire%20to%20scrap%20shops%20and%20vandalizing%20small%20eateries%2C%20most%20of%20which%20belonged%20to%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMobile%20internet%20services%20have%20been%20suspended%20in%20most%20of%20the%20district%2C%20and%20officials%20from%20the%20local%20administration%20in%20Nuh%20are%20investigating%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20initial%20standoff%20that%20sparked%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestions%20linger%20over%20why%20the%20police%20did%20not%20act%20on%20the%20brewing%20tension%20on%20social%20media%2C%20why%20Monu%20Manesar%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20found%20and%20arrested%2C%20and%20why%20they%20failed%20to%20anticipate%20communal%20tension%20in%20a%20sensitive%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690956420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F2jnsuq1o_monu-manesar-ndtv_625x300_02_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmonu-manesar-cow-vigilantes-video-police-moves-in-focus-after-haryana-violence-4261127%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chaudhary%20Aftab%20Ahmed%2C%20the%20MLA%20from%20Haryana's%20Nuh%2C%20said%20authorities%20had%20been%20alerted%20to%20the%20brewing%20tension%20on%20social%20media.%22%2C%22author%22