ily%20fluid%20samples%20and%20serums%3B%20and%20thousands%20of%20vials%20of%20unlabeled%20fluids%20and%20suspected%20biological%20material%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20800%20of%20the%20mice%20found%20inside%20the%20warehouse%20were%20euthanized%20by%20officials%2C%20per%20%3Cem%3ENBC%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Approximately%20175%20mice%20were%20already%20dead%20when%20they%20were%20discovered.%20Joe%20Prado%2C%20the%20Fresno%20County%20Department%20of%20Public%20Health%2C%20said%20the%20site%20was%20also%20filled%20with%20bottles%20of%20%26quot%3Bunknown%20chemicals%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20the%20biohazards%20present%20in%20the%20lab%20have%20been%20destroyed%20as%20of%207%20July%2C%20according%20to%20the%20reports.%20An%20investigation%20into%20the%20lab's%20origins%20is%20underway.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690954380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F85g4hu6_medical-lab-generic_625x300_02_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fillegal-lab-in-us-stored-bioengineered-mice-and-infectious-agents-like-hiv-herpes-4261279%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Officials%20in%20the%20United%20States%20have%20uncovered%20an%20illegal%20medical%20lab%20inside%20a%20California%20warehouse%20filled%20with%20infectious%20agents%2C%20hundreds%20of%20dead%20mice%20and%20other%20hazardous%20materials.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fillegal-lab-in-us-stored-bioengineered-mice-and-infectious-agents-like-hiv-herpes-4261279%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fillegal-lab-in-us-stored-bioengineered-mice-and-infectious-agents-like-hiv-herpes-4261279%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fillegal-lab-in-us-stored-bioengineered-mice-and-infectious-agents-like-hiv-herpes-4261279%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Rajiv%20Gandhi's%20Reach-Out%20To%20RSS%20Had%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20Approval%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20narratives%20of%20present%20day%20Congress%20strategy%20against%20Narendra%20Modi%20appear%20to%20contradict%20the%20Grand%20Old%20Party's%20past%20stance%2C%20as%20revealed%20by%20a%20forthcoming%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20Prime%20Ministers%20Decide%26quot%3B%2C%20by%20veteran%20scribe%20Neerja%20Chowdhury.%20In%20a%20well-researched%20narrative%2C%20she%20recounts%20connections%20between%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20leadership.%20She%20also%20gives%20an%20account%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20cordial%20relationship%20with%20India's%20business%20community.%20This%20is%20in%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20the%20Rahul%20Gandhi-era%20Congress's%20malignancy%20towards%20the%20RSS.%20The%20criticism%20that%20the%20present%20government%20is%20influenced%20by%20a%20few%20%26quot%3Bfavoured%20businesspersons%26quot%3B%20is%20also%20called%20into%20question%20by%20the%20book's%20recapitulation%20of%20events%20in%20the%20life%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20which%20were%20influenced%20by%20a%20business%20house.%20The%20type%20of%20influence%20that%20businesses%20wielded%20in%20the%20Indira%20and%20Rajiv%20eras%20are%20perhaps%20not%20in%20vogue%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20says%20that%20Rajiv%20Gandhi's%20meetings%20with%20then%20RSS%20chief%20Balasaheb%20Deoras'%20brother%2C%20Murlidhar%20Dattatreya%20Deoras%2C%20popularly%20known%20as%20Bhaurao%20Deoras%2C%20had%20the%20approval%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20The%20meetings%20were%20held%20at%20the%20residences%20of%20intermediaries%2C%20promoters%20of%20Mohan%20Meakins%2C%20and%20India's%20leading%20liquor%20manufacturers%20of%20the%20time.%20Owner%20Kapil%20Mohan's%20home%20at%2046%20Pusa%20Road%20in%20West%20Delhi%20and%20his%20nephew%20Anil%20Bali's%20Friends%20Colony%20home%20were%20venues%20of%20the%20Rajiv-Bhaurao%20rendezvous.%20Bhaurao%20met%20Rajiv%20at%2010%20Janpath%20after%20he%20demitted%20power%20as%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(Relations%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20RSS%20have%20usually%20been%20acrimonious.%20Most%20RSS%20leaders%20were%20jailed%20during%20the%20Emergency.%20Balasaheb%20Deoras%20was%20released%20after%20a%20short%20spell%20in%20prison.%20Mahatma%20Gandhi's%20disciple%20Acharya%20Vinoba%20Bhave%2C%20who%20had%20described%20the%20Emergency%20as%20'Anusashan%20Parv'%2C%20had%20spoken%20to%20Indira%20Gandhi%20prior%20to%20Deoras'%20release.%20Vinoba%20Bhave%20had%20played%20a%20background%20role%20in%20softening%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20attitude%20towards%20RSS.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverruling%20the%20reservations%20proffered%20by%20his%20Information%20Minister%20HKL%20Bhagat%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20accepted%20Bhaurao's%20suggestion%20that%20a%20serial%20on%20Ramayan%20be%20aired%20on%20Doordarshan.%20This%20popular%20serial%20produced%20by%20Ramanand%20Sagar%20set%20the%20tone%20for%20the%20escalation%20of%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%2C%20which%20ultimately%20catapulted%20the%20BJP%20from%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%201984%20to%20the%20status%20of%20India's%20party%20of%20governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mohan%20Meakins%20owners%20also%20influenced%20some%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20religious%20decisions.%20Neerja%20recounts%20how%20Indira%20Gandhi%20decided%20to%20visit%20the%20Shakti%20temple%20of%20Chamunda%20Devi%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh's%20Kangra%20region%20prior%20to%20launching%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20in%20politics.%20The%20Mohan%20family%20had%20cordial%20ties%20with%20the%20Nehrus%3B%C2%A0%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20Narendra%20Mohan%20were%20friends%3B%20Indira%20Gandhi%20considered%20VR%20Mohan%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BRakhi%20brother%26quot%3B%20(at%20one%20stage%20a%20matrimonial%20alliance%20between%20the%20two%20families%20had%20been%20considered)%20and%20she%20made%20him%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP.%20He%20was%20one%20of%20the%20original%20Directors%20of%20Sanjay%20Gandhi's%20Maruti%20venture.%20After%20his%20death%20in%201973%2C%20his%20brother%20Kapil%20Mohan%20inherited%20the%20proximity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapil%20Mohan%20and%20his%20nephew%20Anil%20Bali%20were%20not%20responsible%20for%20the%20Rajiv-Bhaurao%20meetings%20alone.%20The%20government%20of%20Morarji%20Desai%20fell%20in%201979%20as%20a%20result%20of%20powwows%20organised%20by%20the%20Mohans%20between%20Sanjay%20Gandhi%20and%20Raj%20Narain%2C%20which%20charted%20the%20way%20for%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20short-lived%20Charan%20Singh%20regime%20(which%20the%20Indira%20Congress%20supported%20from%20outside)%20and%20the%20subsequent%20return%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi%20as%20Prime%20Minister.%20Raj%20Narain%2C%20whose%20election%20petition%20sent%20Indira%20Gandhi%20out%20of%20power%2C%20was%20used%20as%20a%20fulcrum%20to%20oust%20her%20rivals%20and%20chart%20her%20return%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeerja%20recalls%20that%20the%20Mohan%20family%20planned%20a%20visit%20by%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20accompanied%20by%20Sanjay%20Gandhi%2C%20to%20the%20Chamunda%20Devi%20temple%20on%20June%2022%2C%201980%2C%20and%20it%20was%20called%20off%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20aides%20at%20the%20last%20moment.%20Sanjay%20died%20in%20a%20plane%20crash%20on%20June%2023.%20During%20his%20chautha%20ceremony%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20called%20aside%20Anil%20Bali%20and%20commented%20that%20perhaps%20ill%20fortune%20had%20befallen%20as%20she%20had%20cancelled%20her%20visit.%20She%20decided%20to%20go%20there%20in%20a%20few%20months%20and%20offer%20penance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20planned%20a%20visit%20on%20December%2013%20that%20year%20-%20it%20was%20a%20day%20prior%20to%20Sanjay's%20birth%20anniversary%20on%20the%2014th.%20Mohan%20Meakins%20had%20made%20all%20arrangements%20-%20the%20chief%20ministers%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Punjab%2C%20Ram%20Lal%20Thakur%20and%20Darbara%20Singh%2C%20were%20present.%20So%20was%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Gyani%20Zail%20Singh%2C%20who%2C%20two%20years%20later%2C%20was%20to%20become%20President%20of%20India%20(and%20swear%20in%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20after%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20assassination%20in%201984).%20Indira%20Gandhi%20laid%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20a%20ghat%20on%20the%20Baner%20River%20next%20to%20the%20temple%2C%20built%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20Haridwar's%20Har%20ki%20Pauri.%20The%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20Public%20Works%20Department%20(PWD)%20constructed%20the%20ghat%2C%20supervised%20by%20Minister%20Sukh%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20returning%20from%20the%20Chamunda%20Devi%20temple%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20went%20to%20a%20function%20to%20launch%20National%20Herald's%20Urdu%20venture%2C%20Qaumi%20Awaz%2C%20where%20she%20asked%20Rajiv%20to%20join%20her%20on%20the%20dais.%20This%20was%20reluctant%20Rajiv's%20second%20public%20appearance.%20On%20December%206%2C%20he%20had%20attended%20the%20All%20India%20Congress%20Committee%20session%20in%20Delhi's%20Talkatora%20Stadium%20but%20he%20was%20seated%20in%20the%20front%20row%20as%20part%20of%20the%20audience.%20On%20December%2014%2C%20the%20Indian%20Youth%20Congress%20organised%20a%20memorial%20meeting%20at%20Karol%20Bagh's%20Ajmal%20Khan%20Park.%20Here%20Rajiv%20was%20formally%20introduced%20from%20the%20dais%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%94her%20heir%20apparent%20was%20thus%20anointed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajiv%20Gandhi%20too%20visited%20the%20Chamunda%20temple%20with%20Anil%20Bali%20in%20March%201990%2C%20when%20he%20was%20Leader%20of%20Opposition.%20On%20learning%20about%20the%20Indira%20and%20Rajiv%20visits%2C%20Pranab%20Mukherjee%20too%20prayed%20at%20the%20temple%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20Kangra%20in%201995%20as%20Deputy%20Chairman%2C%20Planning%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proximity%20between%20businesses%20and%20the%20powers%20that%20be%20has%20long%20been%20in%20vogue%20in%20India.%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20was%20close%20to%20Ghanshyam%20Das%20Birla%20and%20Jamnalal%20Bajaj.%20The%20term%20Tata-Birla%20emerged%20in%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20era.%20In%20the%20initial%20days%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20tenure%2C%20as%20her%20relationship%20with%20Indian%20Express%20owner%20Ramnath%20Goenka%20(who%20had%20been%20the%20employer%20of%20her%20husband%20Feroze%20Gandhi)%20soured%2C%20so%20did%20her%20rapport%20with%20a%20large%20section%20of%20the%20Marwari%20business%20community%2C%20who%20were%20perceived%20to%20be%20siding%20with%20Goenka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndira%20Gandhi%20told%20her%20close%20associates%20that%20she%20would%20square%20up%20with%20those%20who%20had%20gone%20against%20her%20by%20facilitating%20the%20growth%20of%20parallel%20businesses.%20On%2014%20January%201980%2C%20the%20evening%20of%20the%20new%20regime's%20swearing%20in%2C%20Delhi's%20Taj%20Mansingh%20was%20the%20venue%20of%20a%20dinner%20hosted%20by%20Dhirubhai%20Ambani%2C%20at%20that%20time%20a%20relatively%20unknown%20Gujarati%20trader-businessman.%20The%20entire%20Union%20cabinet%20was%20present.%20A%20new%20era%2C%20of%20the%20dominance%20of%20Gujaratis%20in%20the%20traditionally%20Marwari-Parsi%20controlled%20landscape%20of%20Indian%20business%2C%20had%20dawned.%20The%20old%20adage%20of%20%26quot%3BTata-Birla%26quot%3B%20to%20describe%20dominant%20businesses%20was%20on%20the%20wane.%20The%20backdrop%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BAmbani-Adani%26quot%3B%20narrative%20of%20today%20was%20set%20in%20the%20Indira-Rajiv%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20regime%20can%20ensure%20economic%20growth%20by%20treating%20businesses%20as%20pariah%20-%20the%20acerbic%20comments%20of%20present%20day%20Congress%20leaders%20are%20at%20variance%20with%20the%20paradigm%20of%20past%20Congress%20rulers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonia%20Gandhi's%20biographer%20Rasheed%20Kidwai%20has%20recounted%20how%20Italian%20businessman%20Ottavio%20Quattrocchi%20and%20his%20spouse%20Maria%20were%20permanent%20guests%20in%20the%20informal%20Sunday%20brunches%20hosted%20by%20Rajiv%20and%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20on%20the%20lawns%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20House.%20Quattrocchi%2C%20who%20first%20figured%20in%20parliament%20discourse%20when%20the%20Thal%20Vaishet%20deal%20of%20Rashtriya%20Chemicals%20and%20Fertilisers%20was%20discussed%20in%20the%20post%20Sanjay%20Gandhi%20days%20of%201980%2C%20figured%20prominently%20in%20l'affaire%20Bofors.%20He%20left%20the%20Indian%20shores%20in%201993.%20Attempts%20by%20the%20CBI%20to%20bring%20him%20before%20Indian%20courts%20came%20to%20naught.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeerja%20Chowdhury's%20book%20revisits%20numerous%20incidents%20of%20the%20pre-Modi%20era%2C%20shedding%20light%20on%20aspects%20of%20the%20past%20that%20offer%20a%20perspective%20on%20the%20present%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690953960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-08%2Findira-gandhi-rajiv-gandhi-afp_650x400_41501574281.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frajiv-gandhi-reach-out-to-rss-had-indira-gandhi-approval-4261266%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20narratives%20of%20present%20day%20Congress%20strategy%20against%20Narendra%20Modi%20appear%20to%20contradict%20the%20Grand%20Old%20Party's%20past%20stance%2C%20as%20revealed%20by%20a%20forthcoming%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20Prime%20Ministers%20Decide%26quot%3B%2C%20by%20veteran%20scribe%20Neerja%20Chowdhury.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frajiv-gandhi-reach-out-to-rss-had-indira-gandhi-approval-4261266%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frajiv-gandhi-reach-out-to-rss-had-indira-gandhi-approval-4261266%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frajiv-gandhi-reach-out-to-rss-had-indira-gandhi-approval-4261266%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22It%20Felt%20Like%20Death%5C%22%3A%20Pooja%20Bhatt%20On%20Her%20Divorce%20From%20Manish%20Makhija%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsearch%3Fsearchtext%3DPooja-Bhatt%5C%22%3EPooja%20Bhatt%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20never%20shied%20away%20from%20speaking%20about%20her%20personal%20life.%20The%20actress%20has%20always%20been%20honest%20about%20her%20battle%20with%20alcoholism%20as%20well%20as%20her%20marriage.%20Now%2C%20as%20a%20contestant%20on%20%3Cem%3EBigg%20Boss%20OTT%3C%2Fem%3E%20too%2C%20Pooja%20Bhatt%20has%20not%20shied%20away%20from%20discussing%20unpleasant%20truths.%20In%20the%20latest%20episode%20of%20the%20reality%20show%2C%20Pooja%20Bhatt%20is%20seen%20discussing%20her%20divorce.%20She%20was%20married%20to%20video%20jockey-%20restaurateur%20Manish%20Makhija.%20Speaking%20to%20fellow%20contestant%20Jiya%20Shankar%2C%20Pooja%20Bhatt%20confessed%20that%20getting%20a%20divorce%20was%20entirely%20her%20decision.%20%E2%80%9CI%20said%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20live%20my%20life%20with%20comfort%20or%20keep%20my%2010%20to%2011%20years%20old%20relationship.%20My%20husband%20was%20not%20a%20bad%20person.%20But%20then%20I%20thought%20I%20had%20lost%20myself%20and%20it%20was%20not%20for%20somebody%20else%20or%20the%20betterment%20of%20life.%20I%20wanted%20myself%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pooja%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20could%20not%20%E2%80%9Clie%20to%20herself%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fbigg-boss-ott-2-alia-bhatt-has-picked-her-favourite-contestant-from-salman-khans-show-4247426%5C%22%3EPooja%20Bhatt%20then%20went%20on%20to%20compare%3C%2Fa%3E%20her%20divorce%20to%20death.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20myself%20back%20but%20what%20did%20I%20do%20after%20that%20to%20hide%20my%20pain%20when%20it's%20an%2011-year-old%20relationship%3F%20It%20was%20called%20off%20suddenly%20and%20it%20felt%20like%20death%20but%20people%20ask%20if%20you%20are%20ok%20and%20people%20prefer%20you%20say%20so.%20And%20later%20you%20go%20and%20hide%20behind%20alcohol%20because%20the%20bottle%20delivers.%20Then%20I%20thought%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20set%20myself%20free%20and%20find%20myself%20but%20I%20drilled%20myself%20more%20into%20a%20bad%20zone.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actress-filmmaker%20also%20explained%20how%20she%20survived%20the%20ordeal.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20that%20phase%20in%20my%20life%20was%20the%20lowest%20phase%20of%20my%20life.%20I%20pushed%20myself%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20pool%20and%20suddenly%20one%20survivor's%20instinct%20crept%20in%20and%20I%20clawed%20my%20way%20out%20and%20said%20%E2%80%98No%20boss%2C%20I%20am%20not%20giving%20up%20on%20myself'.%20That's%20very%20important%20but%20when%20I%20look%20back%20to%20that%20phase%20I%20never%20push%20myself%20away%20from%20it.%20I%20look%20straight%20in%20the%20eye%20and%20said%20yes%20you%20have%20become%20this%20otherwise%20what's%20the%20difference%20between%20a%20bottle%20and%20a%20person.%20So%20now%20the%20universe%20said%20that%20I%20am%20ready%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Pooja%20Bhatt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fbigg-boss-ott-2-pooja-bhatt-on-why-she-never-had-kids-4145767%5C%22%3E%20one%20of%20the%20previous%20episodes%20of%20%3Cem%3EBigg%20Boss%20OTT%202%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3EPooja%20Bhatt%20discussed%20her%20equation%20with%20her%20former%20husband.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20a%20very%20good%20human%20being%2C%20he's%20Capricorn%20and%20that's%20why%20we%20got%20along%20very%20well.%20When%20we%20start%20speaking%20a%20lie%2C%20the%20blame%20game%20starts%20and%20I%20didn't%20want%20that.%20Whatever%20was%20there%20was%20very%20good%20till%20the%20time%20it%20lasted.%20Till%20the%20time%20dignity%20was%20there%20we%20were%20together.%20Then%20we%20parted%20ways%20on%20a%20good%20note%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20They%20were%20married%20from%202003%20to%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20stream%20%3Cem%3EBigg%20Boss%20OTT%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20Jio%20Cinema.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690953840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fnitef6l_pooja-bhatt_625x300_02_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fpooja-bhatt-opens-up-about-her-divorce-calls-it-lowest-phase-of-her-life-4261116%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pooja%20Bhatt%20and%20Manish%20Makhija%20got%20divorced%20in%202014%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fpooja-bhatt-opens-up-about-her-divorce-calls-it-lowest-phase-of-her-life-4261116%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fpooja-bhatt-opens-up-about-her-divorce-calls-it-lowest-phase-of-her-life-4261116%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fpooja-bhatt-opens-up-about-her-divorce-calls-it-lowest-phase-of-her-life-4261116%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20begins%20hearing%20on%20batch%20of%20petitions%20challenging%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690953827000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102338309%2Cimgsize-15090.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsc-begins-hearing-on-batch-of-petitions-challenging-abrogation-of-article-370%2Farticleshow%2F102336566.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20commenced%20hearing%20on%20a%20batch%20of%20petitions%20challenging%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20of%20the%20Constitution%20that%20bestowed%20special%20status%20on%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsc-begins-hearing-on-batch-of-petitions-challenging-abrogation-of-article-370%2Farticleshow%2F102336566.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2