-singh-kanwar-yatras-nuh-violence-religious-yatris-at-nuh-8872070%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Singh%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EKisne%20hathiyar%20diye%20unko%20is%20procession%20mein%20le%20jaane%20ke%20liye%3F%20Koi%20talwar%20leke%20jata%20hai%20procession%20mein%3F%20Lathi-dande%20leke%20jata%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Who%20gave%20weapons%20to%20them%20for%20the%20procession%3F%20Who%20goes%20to%20a%20procession%20carrying%20swords%2C%20or%20sticks)%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20wrong.%20A%20provocation%20took%20place%20from%20this%20side%20too.%20I%20am%20not%20saying%20there%20was%20no%20provocation%20from%20the%20other%20side%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20also%20said%20that%20he%20had%20asked%20chief%20minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20and%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20to%20send%20Central%20forces%20to%20Nuh%20as%20the%20police%20force%20was%20%E2%80%9Cinsufficient%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20is%20playing%20a%20role%20to%20instigate%20matters%2C%20Singh%20alleged.%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9CI%20have%20asked%20the%20police%20to%20probe%20who%20uploaded%20such%20videos.%20Someone%20said%20there%20were%20videos%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%98We%20are%20coming%20for%20this%20religious%20function%2C%20your%20daamad%20(son-in-law)%20is%20coming.%20If%20you%20can%20stop%2C%20stop%20it%E2%80%99.%20If%20such%20irresponsible%20videos%20are%20uploaded%2C%20it%20causes%20a%20negative%20impact.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690951190000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F02100909%2F363822017_848035210018686_7753362644021366810_n.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwho-gave-weapons-to-people-in-a-religious-procession-asks-union-minister%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThis%20%5Bcarrying%20weapons%5D%20is%20wrong.%20A%20provocation%20took%20place%20from%20this%20side%20too.%20I%20am%20not%20saying%20there%20was%20no%20provocation%20from%20the%20other%20side%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rao%20Inderjit%20Singh%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwho-gave-weapons-to-people-in-a-religious-procession-asks-union-minister%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22We%20Don't%20Ask%20For%20Luxury%20But...%5C%22%3A%20Hardik%20Pandya%20Slams%20West%20Indies%20Board%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20stand-in%20skipper%20Hardik%20Pandya%20wasn't%20a%20happy%20man%20despite%20the%20team%20winning%20the%20ODI%20series%202-1.%20Speaking%20at%20the%20post-match%20presentation%20ceremony%2C%20Hardik%20didn't%20flinch%20as%20he%20criticised%20the%20West%20Indies%20board%20for%20failing%20to%20manage%20even%20the%20'basic%20necessities'%20of%20Indian%20cricketers.%20Hardik%20said%20that%20while%20the%20team%20doesn't%20want%20luxuries%2C%20he%20is%20hopeful%20of%20the%20'basics'%20to%20be%20taken%20care%20of%20when%20they%20tour%20the%20Caribbean%20side%20the%20next%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20team%20arrived%20in%20West%20Indies%20for%20a%20long%20tour%2C%20consisting%20of%202%20Tests%2C%203%20ODIs%20and%205%20T20Is.%20The%20T20%20assignment%20is%20yet%20to%20begin%20but%20Hardik%20couldn't%20hold%20his%20frustration%20at%20how%20poor%20things%20were%20managed%20by%20the%20Windies%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20one%20of%20the%20nicest%20grounds%20we%20have%20played.%20Things%20can%20be%20better%20when%20we%20come%20to%20West%20Indies%20next%20time.%20Things%20like%20travel%2C%20hopefully%20the%20West%20Indies%20cricket%20board%20can%20take%20note%20and%20ensure%20that%20there%20are%20no%20hiccups.%20We%20don't%20ask%20for%20luxury%20but%20we%20need%20some%20basic%20necessities%20taken%20care%20of.%20%5BOn%20Rohit's%20part%20in%20the%20series%20win%5D%20Rohit%20can%20have%20the%20full%20(trophy)%2C%26quot%3