0to%20indict%20Trump%20first%20and%20reference%20the%20co-conspirators%20to%20place%20swords%20of%20Damocles%20over%20their%20heads%2C%20pressuring%20them%20to%20cooperate%20in%20the%20future.%20Or%20perhaps%20Smith%20just%20wanted%20to%20do%20more%20investigating%20before%20bringing%20more%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20clear%20that%20cooperation%20from%20any%20of%20these%20six%20people%20would%20be%20extremely%20valuable%20to%20the%20prosecution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20strategy%20in%20not%20charging%20them%20now%20is%20to%20put%20pressure%20on%20them%20and%20get%20them%20to%20cooperate%20and%20ultimately%20flip%20on%20Trump%2C%26quot%3B%20Neama%20Rahmani%2C%20the%20president%20of%20West%20Coast%20Trial%20Lawyers%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20other%20alleged%20co-conspirators%20could%20be%20charged%20in%20the%20future.%20We%20just%20saw%20that%20happen%20in%20the%20classified%20documents%20case%2C%20with%20a%20new%20defendant%20charged%20last%20week.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESmith%20could%20use%20someone%20on%20the%20inside%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Sarah%20Krissoff%2C%20a%20former%20federal%20prosecutor%2C%20told%20Insider%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-3rd-indictment-winnable-not-slam-dunk-legal-experts-2023-8%5C%22%3Ethe%20charges%20against%20Trump%20are%20complicated%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20involve%20esoteric%20legal%20theories.%20A%20former%20president%20has%20never%20been%20charged%20before%20with%20trying%20to%20obstruct%20Congress%20from%20certifying%20an%20election.%20It's%20a%20difficult%20case%20to%20explain%20to%20a%20jury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20folks%20dont%20even%20understand%20the%20electoral%20college%2C%26quot%3B%20Krissoff%2C%20now%20a%20white-collar%20defense%20attorney%20at%20Cozen%20O'Connor%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-are-trump-co-conspirators-january-6-indictment-2023-8%5C%22%3Efive%20known%20alleged%20co-conspirators%20are%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Rudy%20Giuliani%2C%20Trump's%20personal%20lawyer%20who%20baselessly%20advanced%20conspiracy%20theories%20about%20the%20election%20in%20court%20and%20in%20public%3B%20Sidney%20Powell%2C%20a%20conspiracy%20theorist%20who%20pushed%20some%20of%20the%20same%20theories%20with%20Giuliani%20and%20on%20her%20own%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeffrey-clark-trump-power-grab-insurrection-act-indictment-2023-8%5C%22%3EJeffrey%20Clark%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Justice%20Department%20official%20who%20tried%20open%20investigations%20into%20nonexistent%20election%20fraud%3B%20and%20John%20Eastman%20and%20Kenneth%20Chesebro%2C%20two%20lawyers%20who%20tried%20to%20overturn%20the%20election%20with%20discredited%20legal%20theories.%20All%20of%20them%20have%20been%20sanctioned%20by%20legal%20bodies%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-lawyers-sanctioned-by-courts-election-lawsuits-2022-12%5C%22%3Eare%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20disciplinary%20proceedings%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20those%20five%2C%20only%20Giuliani%20has%20testified%20before%20the%20Washington%2C%20DC-based%20grand%20jury%20examining%20election%20interference%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F07%2F11%2Fpolitics%2Fgrand-jury-testimony-list-january-6-trump%2Findex.html%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20an%20exhaustive%20list%20compiled%20by%20CNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20a%20statement%20following%20Giuliani's%20grand%20jury%20appearance%20last%20month%2C%20his%20spokesperson%2C%20Ted%20Goodman%2C%20denied%20that%20he%20flipped%20against%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20order%20to%20'flip'%20on%20President%20Trump%20%E2%80%94%20as%20so%20many%20in%20the%20anti-Trump%20media%20are%20fantasizing%20over%20%E2%80%94%20Mayor%20Giuliani%20would've%20had%20to%20commit%20perjury%20because%20all%20the%20information%20he%20has%20regarding%20this%20case%20points%20to%20President%20Trump's%20innocence%2C%26quot%3