92040058605568%257Ctwgr%255E%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26amp%3Bref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fnymag.com%252Fintelligencer%252F2018%252F08%252Falmost-literal-mob-boss-donald-trump-wants-to-ban-flipping.html%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%228bde1ea36ff19b17efcc0df8e163f2a5%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2280%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkylegriffin1%2Fstatus%2F1032592040058605568%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1032592040058605568%257Ctwgr%255E%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fnymag.com%252Fintelligencer%252F2018%252F08%252Falmost-literal-mob-boss-donald-trump-wants-to-ban-flipping.html%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20said%20in%20a%202018%20interview%20with%20Fox%20News%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BYou%20get%2010%20years%20in%20jail%2C%20but%20if%20you%20say%20bad%20things%20about%20something%20...%20now%20you%20go%20from%2010%20years%20to%2C%20'They're%20a%20national%20hero.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20Weisselberg%20never%20really%20flipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Manhattan%20district%20attorney's%20office%20charged%20Weisselberg%20and%20the%20Trump%20Organization%20with%20a%20litany%20of%20white%20collar%20crimes%20in%202021.%20Weisselberg%20pleaded%20guilty%20and%20testified%20against%20the%20Trump%20Organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20in%20a%20bizarre%20courtroom%20display%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fallen-weisselberg-worst-trump-organization-prosecution-witness-2022-11%5C%22%3Ehis%20testimony%3C%2Fa%3E%20appeared%20deliberately%20wishy-washy.%20He%20coordinated%20his%20testimony%20with%20the%20Trump%20Organization's%20defense%20attorneys%20and%20was%20still%20on%20the%20company's%20payroll%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-orgs-ex-cfo-testifies-eric-trump-bonus-2022-11%5C%22%3Ewith%20the%20chance%20of%20a%20rai