t-indies%2Findia-vs-west-indies-what-batting-advice-virat-kohli-gave-to-hardik-pandya-ahead-of-3rd-odi%2Farticleshow%2F102336063.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Not%20So%20Happy%20With...%5C%22%3A%20Ishan%20Kishan's%20Intriguing%20Remarks%20After%203rd%20ODI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20opener%20Ishan%20Kishan%20was%20disappointed%20that%20he%20did%20not%20capitalise%20on%20his%20half-century%20and%20was%20dismissed%20after%20scoring%2077%20in%20the%20third%20ODI%20match%20against%20West%20Indies.%C2%A0With%20Mukesh%20Kumar's%20early%20breakthrough%20followed%20by%20Shardul%20Thakur's%20clobber%20bowling%2C%20India%20registered%20a%202-1%20series%20win%20against%20West%20Indies%20after%20winning%20the%20third%20ODI%20match%20by%20massive%20200-runs%20at%20the%20Brian%20Lara%20Stadium%20in%20Tarouba%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20outstanding%20opening%20partnership%20of%20143%20runs%20between%20Ishan%20Kishan%20and%20Shubman%20Gill%20guided%20India%20to%20set%20a%20massive%20target%20of%20351%2F5%20against%20WI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20receiving%20the%20'Player%20of%20the%20Series'%20award%2C%20Ishan%20said%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20score%20big%20after%20being%20set.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20so%20happy%20with%20the%20finishing%20that%20I%20gave.%20I%20was%20supposed%20to%20score%20big%20after%20being%20set.%20That's%20what%20my%20seniors%20told%20me%2C%20I%20should've%20stayed%20in%20and%20scored%20big.%20That's%20what%20I'll%20try%20next%20time%2C%20I'll%20get%20set%20in%20the%20middle%20and%20score%20big.%20It's%20important%20at%20this%20level%20to%20get%20set.%20It's%20important%20to%20forget%20the%20last%20game%20and%20start%20from%200.%20I%20was%20thinking%20of%20taking%20it%20one%20ball%20at%20a%20time.%20%5BOn%20Shubman%20Gill%5D%20He's%20a%20tremendous%20player%2C%20I've%20seen%20how%20he%20middles%20the%20ball.%20Seeing%20him%20hitting%20it%20out%20of%20the%20middle%20gives%20me%20a%20lot%20of%20confidence%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Ishan%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlways%20important%20to%20win%20at%20this%20level%2C%20the%20learnings%20from%20these%20games%20are%20important.%20We%20were%20looking%20to%20get%20early%20wickets%2C%20and%20didn't%20let%20any%20ball%20go.%20Everyone%20is%20looking%20very%20positive.%20I've%20played%20a%20few%20tournaments%20here%20and%20I%20know%20how%20the%20wickets%20play%20here%2C%20not%20really%20thinking%20about%20the%20next%20T20%20world%20cup.%20Focussing%20on%20the%20upcoming%20tournaments%2C%20you%20know%20how%20one%20tournament%20can%20change%20your%20life.%20We're%20just%20focussing%20on%20that%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20further%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChasing%20a%20huge%20total%20of%20352%2C%20West%20Indies%20lose%20their%20first%20wicket%20early%20as%C2%A0Mukesh%20Kumar%C2%A0dismissed%20Brandon%20King%20on%20a%20duck%20in%20the%20first%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukesh%20again%20struck%20the%20wicket%2C%20he%20cleared%20up%20WI%20captain%20Shai%20Hope%20at%205.%20Shubman%20Gill%20took%20the%20catch%20at%20the%20slip.%20Suffering%20from%20Mukesh's%20class%20swing%2C%20West%20Indies%20were%2017%2F3%20after%207%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWest%20Indies%20continued%20to%20crumble%20as%20Shardul%20Thakur%20dismissed%20Romario%20Shepherd%20(8)%20on%20a%20bounce%20in%20the%2014th%20over.%20Shepherd%20tried%20a%20pull%20shot%20but%20he%20found%20Unadkat%20in%20the%20deep%20backward%20square.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGudakesh%20Motie%20and%20Alzarri%20Joseph%20bounced%20back%20as%20they%20added%2050%E2%80%93run%20partnership%20in%2047%20balls%20for%20the%209th%20wicket.%20However%2C%20their%20partnership%20came%20to%20an%20end%20after%20Thakur%20dismissed%20Joseph%20at%2026%20with%20a%20bouncer.%20Ishan%20Kishan%20caught%20Joseph%20in%20a%20failed%20pull%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThakur%20picked%20the%20last%20wicket%20by%20clearing%20up%20Jayden%20Seales%20with%20an%20angled%