rbaris%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20he%20is%20a%20democrat%20by%20temperament.%20He%20never%20acts%20(or%20never%20decides%20not%20to%20act)%20without%20seeking%20wide-spread%20advice%20from%20the%20various%20gangs%20within%20his%20eco-system.%20If%20he%20has%20not%20expressed%20himself%20on%20Manipur%20it%20is%20because%20the%20process%20of%20consultation%20remains%20inconclusive.%20Some%20of%20the%20inputs%20received%20so%20far%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ET%3Cstrong%3Ehe%3Cem%3E%20Goli%20Maaro%20Salon%20Ko%3C%2Fem%3E%20Gang%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20believe%20that%20Manipur%20is%20a%20dry-run%20for%20more%20and%20more%20resistance%20to%20our%20Hindutva%20agenda.%20We%20should%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20second-guessing%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20merely%20taking%20matters%20to%20a%20logical%20end.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20company%20are%20trying%20to%20put%20us%20on%20the%20back-foot%20about%20the%20violence.%20We%20should%20not%20give%20the%20impression%20of%20being%20apologetic%20or%20remorseful.%20We%20need%20to%20look%20at%20the%20larger%20picture%2C%20beyond%20Manipur.%20All%20minorities%20must%20be%20made%20to%20realise%20that%20we%20control%20the%20armories%20and%20there%20would%20be%20painful%20consequences%20for%20those%20who%20choose%20to%20resist%20us.%20%3Cem%3EGoli%3C%2Fem%3E%20will%20be%20our%20default%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Nagpur%20Gang%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIt%20needs%20to%20kept%20in%20mind%20that%20ridding%20the%20north-east%C2%A0%20of%20Christian%20institutions%2C%20influence%20and%20interference%20have%20been%20a%20part%20of%20our%20original%20%3Cem%3Etapsaya%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20is%20worth%20remembering%20that%20while%20the%20Islamists%20pose%20an%20open%20challenge%2C%20the%20Christian%20conspiracy%20is%20subtle%20and%20subversive.%20The%20Manipur%20flare-up%20only%20reconfirms%20our%20suspicion%20that%20the%20Church%20chooses%20to%20remain%20in%20an%20adversarial%20mood.%20Hence%2C%20matters%20had%20to%20come%20to%20a%20head%2C%20some%20time%20or%20the%20other.%20There%20will%20always%20be%20some%20unpleasantness.%20In%20our%20view%2C%20Biren%20Singh%20should%20be%20left%20alone%3B%20he%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20man%20of%20guts%2C%20a%20rare%20Hindu%3B%20a%20soldier%20who%20has%20an%20appetite%20for%20violence.%20In%20the%20current%20context%2C%20violence%20is%20both%20curative%20and%20therapeutic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20North%20Block%20Gang%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20In%20our%20book%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Farchive%2Fnation%2Fmanipur-cm-served-as-bsf-constable-in-jalandhar-379953%5C%22%3Ea%20former%20constable%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20any%20day%20preferable%20to%20someone%20else.%20Ipso%20facto%2C%20he%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20violence%2C%20guns%2C%20conflict%2C%20etc.%20Biren%20Singh%20has%20earned%20his%20epaulettes.%20With%20all%20the%20forces%20available%20to%20us%2C%20we%20can%20calibrate%20violence%2C%20assert%20control.%20On%20the%20political%20side%2C%20we%20can%20boast%2C%20at%20least%20in%20internal%20consultations%2C%20of%20having%20updated%20the%20blue-book%20of%20fragmentation.%20Our%20agencies%20are%20on%20top%20of%20the%20game.%20Almost%20every%20single%20political%20outfit%20and%20its%20leaders%20are%20amenable%20to%20our%20manipulation.%20Just%20a%20few%20days%20ago%20we%20had%20neatly%20arranged%20for%20the%20defection%20of%20six%20NCP%20MLAs%20in%20Nagaland%20to%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction.%20We%20are%20confident%20that%20we%20can%20gin%20up%20anxieties%20and%20animosities%20across%20the%20north-east%2C%20scaring%20the%20mainland%20into%20lining%20up%20behind%20our%20Supreme%20Leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cstrong%3ESouth%20Block%20Gang%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EArmed%20forces%20are%20in%20total%20command%20of%20the%20situation.%20We%20have%20only%20one%20point%20of%20concern.%20We%20understand%20that%20in%20that%20famous%20video%2C%20one%20of%20the%20women%20involved%20is%20the%20wife%20of%20a%20Kargil%20veteran.%20A%20certain%20sensitivity%20is%20being%20felt%20among%20the%20%3Cem%3Efauji%20biradari%3C%2Fem%3E.%20We%20suggest%20that%20the%20Honorable%20Prime%20Minister%20can%20possibly%20don%20a%20Kargil%20cap%20for%20his%2015th%C2%A0August%20performance.%20And%2C%20for%20good%20measure%2C%20he%20should%20remind%20the%20nation%20that%20the%20Kargil%20war%20happened%20because%20Pakistan%20thought%20there%20was%20a%20political%20vacuum%20in%20India%20and%20that%20it%20could%20take%20advantage%20of%20%3Cem%3Eadarnia%3C%2Fem%3E%20Vajpayee%20ji%20being%20a%20lame-duck%20prime%20minister.%20We%20shall%20strongly%20urge%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20spin%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20to%20our%20political%20advantage%20and%20educate%20the%20nation%20on%20the%20merits%20of%20a%20strong%2C%20cohesive%20government%20at%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20IT%20Cell%20Gang%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20have%20been%20talking%20to%20our%20friends%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Egodi%3C%2Fem%3E%20media.%20They%20expect%20us%20to%20make%20up%20our%20mind.%20As%20one%20anchor%20put%20it%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20averse%20to%20conflict.%20It%20gives%20us%20good%20eye-balls.%20But%2C%20please%20give%20us%20a%20line%20and%20we%20shall%20manufacture%20the%20narrative%20accordingly.%E2%80%9D%20Our%20media%20friends%20are%20under%20the%20impression%20that%20we%20are%20ambivalent%20and%20confused%20about%20what%20to%20do%20next%20in%20Manipur.%20Also%2C%20we%20shall%20like%20to%20put%20on%20record%20that%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20past%2010%20years%20or%20so%20that%20the%20instrument%20of%20social%20media%20has%20worked%20to%20our%20disadvantage%3B%20our%20side%20has%20taken%20a%20good%20beating.%20However%2C%20we%20shall%20like%20to%20assure%20the%20leadership%20that%20we%20will%20be%20going%20back%20to%20the%20drawing%20board%20and%20re-designing%20our%20strategies%20for%20the%202024%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Bombay%20Club%20(A%20%26amp%3B%20A)%20Gang%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20have%20no%20view%20on%20Manipur.%20We%20are%20not%20in%20the%20business%20of%20righteousness%20or%20moralising%3B%20we%20are%20in%20the%20business%20of%20making%20profit%20out%20of%20%3Cem%3Evikas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20We%20and%20our%20external%20partners%20have%20only%20one%20expectation%3A%20keep%20violence%20under%20control.%20The%20%3Cem%3Efirangi%3C%2Fem%3E%20gets%20upset%20with%20violence%20and%20conflict%20in%20the%20headlines.%C2%A0%20Also%20tighten%20up%20media%20management%3B%20we%20notice%20some%20media%20houses%20are%20feeling%20it%20is%20time%20to%20discover%20%E2%80%9Cobjective%20journalism%E2%80%9D%20as%20we%20approach%C2%A0%202024.%20We%20have%20put%20all%20our%20eggs%20in%20your%20basket%20and%20we%20would%20not%20want%20to%20be%20on%20the%20losing%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Retired%20Foreign%20Service%20Gang%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAt%20the%20very%20outset%2C%20we%20must%20state%20that%20for%20now%20all%20our%20collective%20efforts%20to%20graft%20a%20global%20statesman%20persona%20around%20the%20Honorable%20Prime%20Minister%20have%20been%20neutralised%20by%20the%20Manipur%20noise.%20It%20has%20also%20distracted%2C%20we%20must%20be%20prepared%20to%20concede%2C%20from%20the%20G20%20presidency%20razzmatazz.%20We%20urge%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20control%20the%20damage.%20Only%20he%2C%20neither%20the%20home%20minister%20nor%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20can%20change%20the%20narrative.%20The%20stakes%20are%20very%20high.%20All%20the%20good%20work%20of%20the%20past%20ten%20years%20can%20get%20undone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ball%20is%20now%20firmly%20in%20the%20highest%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAtmanirbhar%20is%20the%20pen-name%20of%20an%20aspiring%20satirist%2C%20who%20irregularly%20contributes%20a%20column%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Fbyline%2Fatmanirbhar%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFrom%20the%20Vishwavguru%20Archives%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20and%20believes%20that%20ridicule%20and%20humour%20are%20central%20to%20freedom%20to%20speech%20and%20expression.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690946155000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F07135349%2FFosp0pfaMAAy29H.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhumour%2Fwith-g20-approaching-dilemma-and-confusion-abound-on-how-modi-must-handle-manipur%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20the%20Vishwaguru%20Archives%3A%20Various%20Gangs%20which%20constitute%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20internal%20decision-making%20ecosystem%20cannot%20seem%20to%20agree%20on%20the%20best%20way%20forward.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhumour%2Fwith-g20-approaching-dilemma-and-confusion-abound-on-how-modi-must-handle-manipur%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sushant%20Singh's%20sister%20shares%20throwback%20pic%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690945937000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102334078%2Cimgsize-114695.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsushant-singh-rajputs-sister-shweta-singh-shares-throwback-pic-of-him-leaves-fans-emotional-see-inside%2Farticleshow%2F102334208.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102334208.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESushant%20Singh%20Rajput's%20sister%20Shweta%20Singh%20recently%20took%20to%20her%20IG%20handle%20to%20share%20a%20throwback%20pic%20of%20the%20late%20actor%2C%20where%20he%20is%20seen%20posing%20on%20a%20bike%2C%20along%20with%20the%20cast%20of%20his%20movie%20M.S.%20Dhoni%3A%20The%20Untold%20Story.%20The%20actor%20allegedly%20died%20by%20suicide%20in%20June%2C%202020.%22%2C%22aut