areholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20would%20like%20to%20state%20that%20there%20is%20no%20communication%2C%20formal%20or%20informal%2C%20from%20the%20RBI%20to%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%20or%20its%20Board%20members%20on%20CEO%20succession%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bank%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20responding%20to%20a%20media%20report%2C%20which%20said%20the%20regulator%20is%20nudging%20the%20bank%20to%20appoint%20an%20outsider%20as%20a%20successor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20said%20that%20the%20RBI%20is%20reviewing%20whether%20the%20stakes%20held%20by%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%20in%20wholly-owned%20insurance%20subsidiaries%20pose%20any%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20earlier%20media%20report%2C%20the%20bank%20has%20engaged%20an%20executive%20search%20firm%20for%20finding%20the%20successor%2C%20and%20KVS%20Manian%20and%20Shanti%20Ekambaram%20were%20among%20the%20internal%20candidates%20in%20the%20fray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20statement%20said%20it%20has%20approvals%20from%20regulators%2C%20including%20the%20RBI%2C%20on%20the%20quantum%20of%20stakes%20it%20holds%20in%20the%20insurance%20arms%2C%20and%20has%20not%20received%20any%20communication%20from%20the%20watchdog%20even%20on%20this%20aspect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20be%20noted%20that%20investors%20have%20shown%20some%20unease%20about%20the%20issue%20of%20Uday%20Kotak's%20successor%20lately%20as%20reflected%20in%20some%20share%20price%20corrections.%20In%20his%20letter%20to%20shareholders%2C%20Kotak%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20over-regulation%20on%20entrepreneurial%20spirit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20the%20financial%20sector%20players%20risk%20becoming%20more%20robotic%2C%20curbing%20the%20entrepreneurial%20flair%20since%20the%20fear%20of%20making%20a%20mistake%20overrides%20the%20joy%20of%20creation%20and%20development.%20While%20we%20need%20'Arjuna's%20eye'%20on%20risk%20management%2C%20we%20must%20prevent%20bureaucratisation%20of%20financial%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20Uday%20Kotak%20had%20written.%20Interestingly%2C%20Uday%20Kotak's%20son%20Jay%20is%20also%20active%20in%20the%20bank%2C%20and%20in%20the%20past%2C%20Mr%20Manian%20said%20that%20his%20role%20in%20the%20bank%20will%20be%20decided%20on%20merit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690945620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fv64402r8_kotak-mahindra-bank_625x300_22_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-communication-from-rbi-on-ceo-succession-kotak-mahindra-bank-4261004%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank's%20current%20CEO%20Uday%20Kotak's%20term%20ends%20in%20December%20this%20year%2C%20and%20as%20per%20RBI's%20new%20rules%20on%20limiting%20the%20tenures%20of%20CEOs%2C%20he%20cannot%20continue%20in%20the%20office.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-communication-from-rbi-on-ceo-succession-kotak-mahindra-bank-4261004%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-communication-from-rbi-on-ceo-succession-kotak-mahindra-bank-4261004%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-communication-from-rbi-on-ceo-succession-kotak-mahindra-bank-4261004%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Full%20text%3A%20Trump%20indictment%20on%20January%206%20charges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690945294000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102333594%2Cimgsize-37468.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ffull-text-donald-trump-indictment-on-january-6-charges%2Farticleshow%2F102333643.cms%22%2C%22summar