2C%20Modi%20and%20Yogi%2C%20these%20are%20the%20two%2C%20and%20your%20Thackeray%E2%80%99)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20civilian%20victims%20have%20been%20identified%20as%C2%A0Abdul%20Qadirbhai%20Mohammed%20Hussain%20Bhanpurwala%2C%20Akhtar%20Abbas%20Ali%2C%20and%20Sadar%20Mohammed%20Hussain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20when%2033-year-old%20Singh%20was%20produced%20before%20a%20magistrate%20court%20in%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Borivali%20Court%2C%20the%20narrative%20was%20diametrically%20opposite%20to%20what%20was%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20The%20remand%20copy%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20make%20any%20mention%20of%20the%20video%20that%20clearly%20shows%20his%20communally%20charged%20speech.%20The%20remand%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20entirely%20focuses%20on%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cillness%E2%80%9D%20and%20indicates%20his%20unstable%20mind%20which%20led%20him%20to%20take%20an%20extreme%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Frailway-protection-force-constable-shoots-dead-asi-three-others-in-train%5C%22%3ERPF%20Constable%20Kills%20Officer%2C%20Three%20Muslim%20Passengers%20in%20Hate%20Crime%20Onboard%20Running%20Train%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20charged%20him%20with%20Section%20302%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20for%20murder%2C%20under%20sections%20of%20the%20Arms%20Act%20and%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20Act.%20Crucial%20sections%20like%20153%20A%2C%20153B%2C%20295%20A%2C%20and%20505%20of%20the%20IPC%20that%20specifically%20look%20at%20hate%20crimes%20and%20communally-%20charged%20offences%20are%20missing%20from%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20August%201%2C%20Singh%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20court%20amid%20high-security.%20Although%20an%20open%20court%2C%20and%20otherwise%20accessible%20to%20everyone%2C%20it%20was%20suddenly%20cordoned%20off.%20Journalists%20gathered%20outside%20the%20court%20were%20denied%20entry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prosecution%20focused%20on%20the%20act%20of%20cold-blooded%20murder%20and%20sought%2014-days%20of%20custody.%20The%20magistrate%20court%20granted%20seven%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20parallel%20move%2C%20%E2%80%9CRailway%20ministry%20sources%E2%80%9D%20in%20Delhi%20have%20provided%20a%20section%20of%20the%20media%20with%20a%20similar%20narrative.%20NDTV%2C%20one%20of%20the%20media%20platforms%20invited%20for%20this%20%E2%80%98briefing%E2%80%99%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frailway-cop-sent-for-mental-health-check-over-killings-no-communal-angle-4259764%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topstories%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20%E2%80%98comprehensive%20mental%20and%20psychological%20health%20assessment%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20RPF%20personnel%20is%20being%20carried%20out%2C%20Railway%20Ministry%20sources%20said.%20They%20have%20ruled%20out%20the%20communal%20angle%20%E2%80%93%20raised%20by%20videos%20and%20posts%20on%20social%20media%20%E2%80%93%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20accused%20had%20also%20shot%20Hindus%2C%20including%20his%20own%20boss.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20reports%20speaks%20of%20%E2%80%98Hindus%E2%80%99%20in%20plural%2C%20Singh%20in%20fact%20shot%20only%20one%20Hindu%2C%20his%20boss.%20He%20then%20moved%20through%20some%20eight%20bogies%20and%20shot%20dead%20three%20men%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20were%20Muslims%20clearly%20identifiable%20by%20their%20facial%20hair%20and%20clothes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20clear%20if%20the%20%E2%80%9Csources%E2%80%9D%20were%20asked%20by%20those%20at%20the%20%E2%80%98briefing%E2%80%99%20to%20explain%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20selection%20of%20targets%20and%20his%20onboard%20comments%20recorded%20on%20video%2C%20and%20if%20they%20were%20asked%2C%20what%20their%20answer%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20does%20the%20remand%20copy%20say%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20along%20with%20three%20others%20%E2%80%93%20Meena%2C%20constable%20Aman%20Ghanshyam%20Acharya%2C%20and%20head%20constable%20Narendra%20Parmar%20%E2%80%93%20was%20on%20escort%20duty.%20At%202%3A53%20am%2C%20when%20the%20Jaipur%20Mumbai%20Superfast%20Express%20entered%20Surat%20station%2C%20the%20armed%20personnel%20entered%20the%20train.%20Singh%20and%20Meena%20were%20assigned%20escort%20duty%20of%20the%20three-tier%20coach%3B%20Acharya%20and%20Parmar%20were%20to%20man%20the%20sleeper%20coaches.%20Acharya%2C%20who%20is%20now%20the%20complainant%20in%20the%20case%2C%20has%20claimed%20in%20his%20statement%20that%20a%20few%20minutes%20after%20entering%20the%20train%2C%20Singh%20had%20complained%20of%20bad%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20complained%20to%20Meena%20that%20he%20was%20not%20keeping%20well%20and%20wanted%20to%20deboard%20the%20train%20at%20Valsad.%20Meena%20had%20tried%20telling%20him%20that%20his%20shift%20is%20soon%20coming%20to%20an%20end%20and%20he%20should%20stay%20back%20till%20the%20train%20reached%20Mumbai%2C%E2%80%9D%20Acharya%E2%80%99s%20statement%2C%20which%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20remand%20copy%2C%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcharya%20further%20claims%20that%20Singh%20%E2%80%9Clooked%20angry%E2%80%9D%20and%20unconvinced%20with%20Meena%E2%80%99s%20suggestion%3B%20he%20had%20insisted%20Meena%20call%20up%20another%20senior%2C%20Sujit%20Kumar%20Pandey.%20Pandey%20too%2C%20Acharya%20claims%2C%20had%20directed%20Singh%20to%20stay%20back%20and%20complete%20his%20full%20duty%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Singh%20was%20not%20convinced%2C%20Acharya%20says%2C%20Meena%20asked%20him%20to%20go%20to%20the%20nearby%20B-4%20coach.%20%E2%80%9CI%20sat%20close%20by%20as%20Singh%20rested%20on%20one%20of%20the%20empty%20seats%2C%E2%80%9D%20Acharya%20claims%20in%20his%20statement.%20Here%2C%20Acharya%20says%2C%20Singh%20stayed%20only%20for%2010%20minutes%20and%20demanded%20his%20service%20rifle.%20When%20Acharya%20refused%2C%20Singh%20allegedly%20snatched%20the%20rifle.%20Until%20this%20point%2C%20Acharya%2C%20who%20had%20completed%20his%20supervision%20duty%20and%20returned%20to%20Meena%2C%20had%20witnessed%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcharya%20claims%20Singh%20snatched%20the%20rifle%20and%20walked%20away.%20This%20was%20around%205%20am.%20Around%205%3A25%20am%2C%20Meena%20was%20shot%20dead.%20Acharya%2C%20who%20was%20afraid%20of%20being%20targeted%20by%20a%20visibly%20enraged%20Singh%2C%20claims%20to%20have%20hidden%20in%20a%20sleeper%20coach%20as%20he%20saw%20Singh%20walk%20towards%20him%20at%20one%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20passengers%20began%20to%20run%20helter-skelter%2C%20someone%20pulled%20the%20train%E2%80%99s%20emergency%20chain.%20Acharya%20looked%20up%20a%20train%20app%20and%20found%20out%20that%20the%20train%20had%20now%20entered%20Mumbai%20and%20had%20halted%20between%20Mira%20Road%20and%20Dahisar%20station.%20%E2%80%9CI%20walked%20towards%20B-6%20coach%20and%20found%20one%20man%20lying%20in%20%5Ba%5D%20pool%20of%20blood.%20Another%20man%20was%20lying%20in%20the%20pantry%20car%2C%E2%80%9D%20Acharya%E2%80%99s%20statement%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20mention%20of%20communally-charged%20video%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcharya%2C%20besides%20being%20a%20colleague%2C%20is%20also%20someone%20who%20closely%20saw%20what%20transpired%20on%20the%20train.%20As%20a%20complainant%2C%20his%20statements%20are%20crucial.%20The%20first%20information%20report%20is%20based%20on%20what%20he%20witnessed.%20But%20between%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20(that%20happened%20soon%20after%20the%20train%20halted%20and%20Singh%20ran%20towards%20Mira%20Road%20railway%20station)%20and%20his%20production%20before%20the%20magistrate%20court%2C%20the%20police%20had%20over%2024%20hours%20to%20gather%20witness%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20videos%20were%20already%20public%2C%20one%20can%20safely%20presume%20the%20police%20too%20had%20access%20to%20them.%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20statements%20are%20audible%20and%20are%20communally%20charged.%20In%20the%20less%20than%20one-minute%20video%20that%20was%20circulated%20on%20social%20media%2C%20Singh%20is%20heard%20speaking%20about%20Pakistan%20and%20clearly%20declaring%20that%20if%20one%20has%20to%20live%20in%20India%2C%20Modi%20(Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi)%20and%20Yogi%20(Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath)%20were%20the%20only%20way%20forward.%20The%20remand%20makes%20no%20mention%20of%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20BJP%20MLA%20Manisha%20Chaudhary%2C%20who%20visited%20the%20Borivali%20GRP%2C%20had%20told%20the%20media%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20thorough%20investigation%20must%20be%20carried%20out%20to%20ascertain%20the%20exact%20reason%20behind%20the%20incident.%20It%20must%20be%20found%20out%20if%20the%20accused%20was%20under%20depression%20or%20if%20he%20was%20disturbed.%E2%80%9D%20Chaudhary%20spoke%20of%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cmental%20illness%E2%80%9D%20even%20before%20the%20police%20had%20ascertained%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20has%20meanwhile%20written%20to%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20asking%20them%20to%20take%20the%20video%20of%20Singh%20and%20of%20the%20slain%20men%E2%80%99s%20bodies%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20no%20time%2C%20the%20official%20narrative%20was%20relayed%20by%20many%20media%20channels%20%E2%80%93%20some%20even%20running%20a%20primetime%20discussion%20over%20his%20mental%20health.%20His%20lawyers%2C%20Amit%20A%20Mishra%20and%20Surendra%20A%20Landage%2C%20too%2C%20argued%20before%20the%20court%20that%20Singh%20was%20of%20unstable%20and%20unsound%20mind%20%E2%80%93%20an%20alibi%20that%20would%20help%20him%20a%20great%20deal%20in%20the%20case.%20Mishra%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Singh%20looked%20%E2%80%9Cdepressed%20in%20court%E2%80%9D.%20Landage%20told%20the%20media%2C%20g