cases%20of%20January%206%2C%202021%2C%20defendants%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20the%20only%20federal%20judge%20in%20the%20District%20of%20Columbia%20that%20has%20sentenced%20January%206%20rioters%20to%20longer%20sentences%20than%20prosecutors%20have%20requested%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fdonald-trump%2Flive-blog%2Ftrump-live-updates-grand-jury-2020-election-probe-arrives-courthouse-rcna96825%5C%22%3ENBC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20In%20one%20instance%2C%20Chutkan%20sentenced%20January%206%20rioter%20Matthew%20Mazzocco%20to%2045%20days%20in%20jail%20despite%20prosecutors'%20requests%20for%20home%20confinement%20for%20the%20duration%20of%20his%20sentence%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudge-sentences-capitol-riot-defendant-to-jail-as-warning-to-others%5C%22%3EInsider%20previously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20the%20country%20is%20watching%2C%26quot%3B%20Insider%20reported%20she%20said%20during%20the%20sentencing%2C%20%26quot%3Bto%20see%20what%20the%20consequences%20are%20for%20something%20that%20has%20not%20ever%20happened%20in%20this%20country%20before%2C%20for%20actions%20and%20crimes%20that%20undermine%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20our%20democracy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChutkan%20has%20also%20previously%20rejected%20a%20request%20by%20Trump's%20legal%20team%20to%20block%20the%20release%20of%20documents%20to%20the%20House%20committee%20investigating%20the%20January%206%2C%202021%2C%20Capitol%20riot%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FPolitics%2Ftanya-chutkan-judge-assigned-latest-trump-case%2Fstory%3Fid%3D101922597%5C%22%3EABC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20maintained%20his%20innocence%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20charges%20against%20him%2C%20publicly%20calling%20the%20investigations%20into%20his%20behavior%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com