0that%20the%20%26quot%3B35-year%20mark%20is%20significant%20because%20it%20is%20when%20you%20enter%20the%20peak%20of%20your%20earning%20capability.%26quot%3B%20Lennon%20believes%20this%20trend%20could%20create%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20problems%26quot%3B%20in%20Chinese%20society%20if%20people%20don't%20earn%20enough%20to%20build%20up%20their%20financial%20reserves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlready%2C%20some%20have%20voiced%20their%20worries%20about%20being%20forcibly%20aged%20out%20of%20the%20workforce.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20turned%2034%20and%20lost%20my%20job%20three%20months%20ago.%20Will%20I%20be%20able%20to%20survive%20this%20year%3F%26quot%3B%20one%20person%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F5158040197%2FN9Artopfp%3Frefer_flag%3D1001030103_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Weibo.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20%26quot%3BCurse%20of%2035%26quot%3B%20is%20an%20offshoot%20of%20China's%20grueling%20%26quot%3B996%26quot%3B%20work%20culture%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20preference%20for%20younger%20workers%20is%20in%20part%20due%20to%20a%20workplace%20culture%20that%20requires%20people%20to%20clock%20long%20hours%20on%20the%20job.%20Better%20known%20as%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F996-work-culture-schedule-popular-in-china-explained-2021-7%5C%22%3E996%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Chinese%20workers%20who%20want%20to%20get%20ahead%20are%20expected%20to%20observe%20a%20punishing%20schedule%2C%20working%20from%209%20a.m.%20to%209%20p.m.%2C%20six%20days%20a%20week.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20such%2C%20employers%20favor%20those%20who%20are%20young%2C%20healthy%2C%20and%20willing%20to%20pull%20long%20hours%20for%20the%20hustle%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYounger%20workers%20are%20indeed%20in%20better%20health%20conditions%20than%20those%20who%20are%20older%2C%20and%20they%20tend%20to%20have%20fewer%20family%20obligations%20than%20those%20aged%20above%20