several%20of%20the%20individuals%20designed%20have%20planned%20or%20carried%20out%20attacks%20that%20targeted%20journalists%20and%20local%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTreasury%E2%80%99s%20actions%20today%20against%20ISIS%20and%20al-Qa%E2%80%99ida%20operatives%20and%20facilitators%20continue%20our%20efforts%20to%20help%20prevent%20and%20disrupt%20financial%20and%20other%20support%20for%20terrorist%20attacks%20globally.%20The%20United%20States%20is%20committed%20to%20denying%20funding%20and%20resources%20to%20these%20terrorist%20support%20networks%20and%20countering%20the%20threats%20they%20pose%20both%20locally%20and%20internationally%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20Under%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Treasury%20for%20Terrorism%20and%20Financial%20Intelligence%20Brian%20E%20Nelson%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20US%20government%E2%80%99s%20action%2C%20all%20property%20and%20interests%20in%20the%20property%20of%20the%20designated%20persons%20that%20are%20in%20the%20US%20or%20in%20control%20of%20US%20nationals%20are%20blocked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20addition%2C%20financial%20institutions%20and%20other%20persons%20that%20engage%20in%20certain%20transactions%20or%20activities%20with%20the%20sanctioned%20entities%20and%20individuals%20may%20expose%20themselves%20to%20sanctions%20or%20be%20subject%20to%20an%20enforcement%20action%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20OFAC%20press%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20listed%20individuals%20include%20members%20of%20an%20ISIS-affiliated%20cell%20in%20Maldives%E2%80%99%20second%20largest%20city%2C%20Addu%20City%2C%20that%20had%20%E2%80%9Cattempted%20to%20carry%20out%20terror%20plots%20since%20at%20least%202018%2C%20including%20attacks%20utilising%20improvised%20explosive%20devices%20(IEDs)%20and%20Unmanned%20Aerial%20Vehicles%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20three%20individuals%20were%20in%20an%20ISIS-aligned%20criminal%20gang%20Kuda%20Henveyru%20that%20%E2%80%9Ccarried%20out%20organised%20large-sc