04%2F16125509%2FScreenshot-2023-04-16-at-12.55.00-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFormer%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20governor%20Satyapal%20Malik%20said%20the%20violence%20that%20began%20in%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20Nuh%20and%20spread%20to%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20state%20was%20not%20spontaneous.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20the%20attacks%20in%20seven%20to%20eight%20different%20places%20were%20well-coordinated%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20creating%20a%20communal%20divide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20country%20will%20burn%20like%20Manipur%20if%20these%20people%20are%20not%20contained%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CJats%20by%20culture%20or%20tradition%20believe%20in%20the%20Arya%20Samaj%20way%20of%20life%20and%20are%20not%20very%20religious%20in%20the%20traditional%20sense%20of%20the%20term.%20Neither%20are%20the%20Muslims%20of%20this%20area%20very%20traditional%20in%20their%20outlook.%20Therefore%20one%20has%20never%20heard%20of%20the%20two%20communities%20clashing%20in%20this%20manner%20ever%20since%20Independence.%20And%20these%20attacks%20will%20only%20increase%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%202024%20as%20is%20evident%20in%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20addressing%20a%20packed%20hall%20at%20the%20Constitution%20Club.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20convention%20on%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20security%20affairs%E2%80%9D%2C%20organised%20by%20six%20groups%20of%20social%20activists%2C%20also%20passed%20two%20resolutions%20on%20the%20Pulwama%20and%20the%20Balakot%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20demanded%20the%20government%20to%20make%20the%20Pulwama%20attack%20report%20public%20along%20with%20an%20action-taken%20report%2C%20including%20a%20white%20paper%20on%20the%20lapses%20and%20action%20taken%20against%20those%20involved.%20They%20also%20said%20a%20Supreme%20Court-monitored%20committee%20should%20probe%20the%20Pulwama%20tragedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20assembled%20also%20demanded%20an%20increase%20in%20security%20at%20various%20pilgrim%20sites.%20They%20feared%20that%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20an%20attack%20could%20be%20carried%20out%20on%20the%20under-construction%20Ram%20Mandir%20at%20Ayodhya%20or%20any%20of%20the%20other%20prominent%20temples%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20could%20be%20done%20by%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20to%20polarise%20the%20public%20and%20win%20the%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20Malik%20said.%20An%20alleged%20threat%20by%20Al-Qaeda%20that%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20would%20be%20blown%20up%20should%20be%20taken%20seriously%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gathering%20was%20addressed%20by%20Members%20of%20Parliament%2C%20Digvijay%20Singh%2C%20Danish%20Ali%2C%20Kumar%20Ketkar%2C%20John%20Brittas%2C%20and%20lawyer%20Prashant%20Bhushan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20going%20by%20the%20audience%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20Satyapal%20Malik%E2%80%99s%20speech%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20interest%20in%20what%20happened%20at%20Pulwama%20or%20Balakot%20has%20not%20waned.%20While%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20allegations%20that%20the%20Pulwama%20attack%20was%20done%20by%20the%20Indian%20establishment%20were%20discussed%20in%20whispers%2C%20now%20all%20prominent%20speakers%20openly%20voiced%20their%20apprehension%20that%20the%20attack%20was%20not%20from%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20Pulwama%2C%20Modi%20milked%20the%20tragedy%20and%20told%20crowds%20to%20remember%20Pulwama%20when%20they%20vote.%20I%20tell%20the%20crowds%20once%20again%2C%20remember%20Pulwama%20when%20you%20vote%20this%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Malik.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20several%20unanswered%20questions.%20Where%20did%20the%20RDX%20come%20from%3F%20Why%20was%20the%20route%20not%20sanitised%20or%20manned%20by%20anyone%20for%2010%20kilometres%20either%20side%3F%20Why%20was%20the%20aircraft%20refused%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContradicting%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20who%20said%20there%20were%2011%20intelligence%20reports%20ahead%20of%20the%20attack%2C%20Malik%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20governor%2C%20I%20used%20to%20get%20three%20intelligence%20reports%20a%20day%2C%20each%20detailing%20a%20terror%20attack%20that%20could%20happen%20to%20me%20or%20to%20the%20establishment.%20I%20was%20warned%20by%20the%20Army%20not%20to%20travel%20by%20road%20but%20take%20a%20chopper%20and%20so%20on.%20There%20was%20not%20a%20single%20intelligence%20report%20that%20an%20Army%20convoy%20could%20be%20attacked%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMalik%20said%20something%20similar%20could%20be%20planned%20in%202024.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20could%20kill%20a%20prominent%20BJP%20leader%20or%20throw%20a%20bomb%20at%20the%20Ram%20Mandir.%20Why%20is%20Ajit%20Doval%20(National%20Security%20Advisor)%20frequenting%20the%20UAE%20now%20a%20days%3F%20He%20is%20drumming%20up%20support%20from%20the%20rulers%20there%20that%20they%20should%20put%20pressure%20on%20the%20Pakistanis%20not%20to%20retaliate%20when%20our%20troops%20enter%20Pakistan%20Occupied%20Kashmir.%20They%20will%20stay%20there%20for%20a%20few%20days%20and%20come%20back%20and%20hope%20to%20win%20the%20election.%20People%20should%20know%20what%20they%20are%20up%20to%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690910397000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F16125509%2FScreenshot-2023-04-16-at-12.55.00-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnuh-clashes-well-coordinated-more-such-violence-likely-ahead-of-2024-polls-satyapal-malik%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'The%20whole%20country%20will%20burn%20like%20Manipur%20if%20these%20people%20are%20not%20contained%2C'%20the%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20governor%20said%2C%20in%20an%20apparent%20reference%20to%20the%20Modi%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnuh-clashes-well-coordinated-more-such-violence-likely-ahead-of-2024-polls-sa