t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20said%20that%20the%20provisional%20diagnosis%20of%20deaths%20points%20towards%20%E2%80%9Cnatural%20causes%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20none%20of%20the%20cheetahs%20have%20died%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Cunnatural%20causes%E2%80%9D%20such%20as%20poaching%2C%20snaring%2C%20poisoning%2C%20road%20hits%2C%20electrocution%2C%20etc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20respectfully%20submitted%20that%20the%20NTCA%20today%20has%20no%20reason%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20mortalities%20were%20caused%20on%20account%20of%20any%20inherent%20unsuitability%20at%20the%20Kuno%20site%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20affidavit%20said%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Flegal%2Fcheetah-deaths-at-kuno-national-park-troubling-but-not-unduly-alarming-ntca-to-sc%2F621263.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPTI%20report%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20affidavit%20also%20claimed%20that%20cheetahs%20have%20a%20very%20low%20survival%20rate%20even%20in%20non-introduced%20or%20native%20populations.%20In%20introduced%20populations%2C%20the%20survival%20rates%20are%20even%20lower%2C%20it%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20case%20of%20introduced%20population%2C%20the%20survival%20rates%20are%20even%20much%20lower%20taking%20other%20variables%20into%20account%20which%20may%20lead%20to%20about%2010%25%20survival%20in%20cubs%2C%20and%20thus%2C%20mortalities%20(at%20KNP)%20though%20troubling%20and%20in%20need%20of%20redressal%20and%20curtailment%20are%20not%20unduly%20alarming%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPTI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20quoted%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Flegal%2Fcheetah-deaths-at-kuno-national-park-troubling-but-not-unduly-alarming-ntca-to-sc%2F621263.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaffidavit%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20saying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFurther%2C%20for%20veterinary%20care%2C%20day-to-day%20management%20and%20monitoring%20and%20other%20specific%20aspects%20related%20to%20ecology%20and%20behaviour%20of%20cheetahs%20is%20being%20done%20in%20consultation%20with%20internationally%20experienced%20cheetah%20experts%2C%20when%20and%20where%20required%2C%20and%20in%20conformity%20with%20the%20scientific%20Action%20Plan.%20The%20best%20possible%20veterinary%20support%20and%20health%20care%20is%20provided%20to%20the%20cheetahs%20to%20ensure%20their%20survival%20in%20the%20natural%20ecosystem%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20affidavit%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Flegal%2Fcheetah-deaths-at-kuno-national-park-troubling-but-not-unduly-alarming-ntca-to-sc%2F621263.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20have%20said.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20prophylactic%20treatment%20is%20being%20administered%20to%20all%20surviving%20cheetahs%20and%20that%20a%20review%20of%20project%20implementation%20is%20being%20undertaken.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdrian%20Tordiffe%2C%20South%20African%20wildlife%20veterinarian%20who%20is%20also%20on%20the%20Cheetah%20Project%20Steering%20Committee%20had%20first%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20level%20of%20veterinary%20care%20available%20at%20Kuno%20while%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fproject-cheetah-deaths-radio-collar-infections%5D%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Espeaking%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20July%2015.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETordiffe%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Rajesh%20Gopal%2C%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Steering%20Committee%2C%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fproject-cheetah-deaths-radio-collar-infections%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ealso%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20deaths%20of%20two%20adult%20cheetahs%2C%20Tejas%20and%20Suraj%2C%20were%20caused%20by%20radio%20collar-caused%20infections.%20The%20NTCA%20on%20July%2016%20had%20denied%20this%20claim%20and%20insisted%20that%20all%20animals%20died%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Cnatural%20causes%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIdentified%20other%20sites%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20joint%20affidavit%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Flegal%2Fkuno-deaths-govt-identifies-potential-sites-in-mp-rajasthan-for-cheetah-introduction%2F621328.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20apart%20from%20Kuno%20National%20Park%2C%20authorities%20have%20identified%20potential%20sites%20for%20cheetah%20introduction%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan.%20These%20include%20Gandhi%20Sagar%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary%20and%20Nauradehi%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Shahgarh%20Bulge%2C%20Bhainsrorgarh%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary%20and%20enclosure%20of%20Mukundra%20Hills%20Tiger%20Reserve%20in%20Rajasthan.%20However%2C%20Mukundra%20Hills%20is%20at%20present%20not%20fit%20for%20accommodating%20cheetahs%2C%20per%20the%20affidavit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%20Kuno%20National%20Park%20and%20its%20extended%20landscape%20of%206800%20per%20sq.km%2C%20the%20NTCA%20has%20requested%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20on%20June%2028%20to%20add%20areas%20in%20Shivpuri%2C%20Sheopur%20divisions%20and%20Heerupur%20wildlife%20sanctuary%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Finquiry-into-cheetahs-deaths-points-to-natural-causes-centre-informs-sc%2Farticle67143291.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Currently%2C%20Gandhi%20Sagar%20and%20Nauradehi%20are%20being%20prepared%