er's%20Claim%20That%20People%20Were%20'Held%20Hostage'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01204256%2FTemple.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENuh%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20A%20day%20after%20Haryana%20home%20minister%20Anil%20Vij%20said%20that%20around%20%E2%80%9C3000-4000%20persons%20were%20held%20hostage%20in%20a%20temple%E2%80%9D%20allegedly%20by%20Muslim%20rioters%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fharyana-at-least-1-killed-5-injured-as-clashes-breakout-during-rally-by-hindutva-outfits-in-nuh%5C%22%3Ecommunal%20clashes%20in%20Nuh%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20priest%20of%20the%20same%20temple%20refuted%20such%20a%20claim.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EDeepak%20Sharma%2C%20priest%20of%20the%20Nalhar%20Mahadev%20temple%20where%20Vij%20claimed%20that%20people%20had%20been%20%E2%80%9Cheld%20hostage%E2%80%9D%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20flow%20of%20pilgrims%20in%20the%20temple%20is%20generally%20high%20in%20the%20month%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESaawan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(considered%20holy%20for%20Lord%20Shiva%20devotees).%20Because%20of%20the%20Shobha%20Yatra%20on%20Monday%20(that%20is%20considered%20a%20sacred%20day%20for%20Shiva%E2%80%99s%20devotees)%2C%20the%20number%20of%20devotees%20was%20very%20high.%20They%20kept%20coming%20in%20and%20going%20out%20(after%20offering%20their%20prayers)%20during%20the%20Shobha%20Yatra.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELogon%20ko%20bandhak%20kya%20banayenge%2C%20parmaatma%20ki%20sharan%20mein%20the.%20Achanak%20pata%20chala%20ki%20mahaul%20kharaab%20hai.%20Stithi%20Kharab%20hone%20ki%20wajah%20se%20andar%20fans%20gaye%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(How%20is%20it%20possible%20to%20keep%20these%20people%20hostage%3F%20They%20were%20in%20the%20shelter%20of%20the%20almighty.%20But%20suddenly%20they%20got%20to%20know%20that%20the%20situation%20outside%20is%20not%20good.%20Since%20the%20situation%20outside%20became%20bad%2C%20people%20got%20trapped%20inside%20(the%20temple)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sharma%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0when%20asked%20whether%20devotees%20were%20%E2%80%9Cheld%20hostage%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20claim%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20clashes%20were%20still%20unfolding%20had%20created%20an%20alarm%20on%20Monday%20regarding%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20clashes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Nalhar%20Mahadev%20Temple%20is%20located%20far%20from%20the%20main%20town%20of%20Nuh.%20It%20is%20surrounded%20by%20hills%2C%20and%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20in%20existence%20since%20the%20time%20of%20Pandavas%2C%20the%20mythical%20heroes%20of%20Mahabharata.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fharyana-at-least-1-killed-5-injured-as-clashes-breakout-during-rally-by-hindutva-outfits-in-nuh%5C%22%3EHaryana%3A%20At%20Least%203%20Killed%2C%2020%20Injured%20as%20Clashes%20Breakout%20During%20Rally%20by%20Hindutva%20Outfits%20in%20Nuh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENuh%20saw%20communal%20clashes%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20on%20Monday%20when%20a%20belligerent%20religious%20procession%20called%20Brijmandal%20Jalabhishek%20Yatra%20organised%20by%20Hindutva%20groups%20Bajrang%20Dal%20and%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20was%20passing%20through%20Nuh.%20In%20the%20build-up%20to%20the%20Yatra%2C%20several%20hateful%20videos%20by%20Hindutva%20activists%20were%20circulated%20in%20the%20region%2C%20following%20which%20similar%20videos%20made%20by%20some%20Muslim%20youth%20daring%20Hindutva%20activists%20like%20Monu%20Manesar%20to%20enter%20Nuh%20also%20surfaced%20on%20social%20media.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20police%20claimed%20that%20a%20mob%20tried%20to%20violently%20stop%20the%20Yatra%20in%20Nuh%20because%20of%20which%20a%20fight%20broke%20out%20and%20later%20escalated%20into%20a%20full-blown%20communal%20riot.%20The%20residual%20effect%20of%20the%20clashes%20was%20also%20seen%20in%20adjoining%20Gurugram%20where%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fgurugram-mosque-set-on-fire-was-the-only-one-of-govt-allocated-land-in-the-area%5C%22%3Emosque%20was%20set%20on%20fire%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20late%20evening.%20One%20of%20the%20imams%20of%20the%20mosque%20was%20also%20shot%20dead%20by%20a%20mob.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20since%20the%20clashes%20broke%20out%2C%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20tried%20to%20fuel%20the%20communal%20animosity%20in%20the%20area%2C%20with%20even%20home%20minister%20Vij%20demanding%20the%20deployment%20of%20central%20forces%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20Congress%20legislators%20of%20the%20region%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20have%20been%20appealing%20for%20peace%20and%20working%20closely%20with%20the%20district%20administration%20to%20prevent%20another%20such%20flare-up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F12211258%2FAnil_Vij_PTI.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F12211258%2FAnil_Vij_PTI.jpeg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F12211258%2FAnil_Vij_PTI-300x150.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F12211258%2FAnil_Vij_PTI-800x400.jpeg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-522137%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EHaryana%20home%20minister%20Anil%20Vij.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%2FFile%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Mewat%20and%20Gurugram%20regions%20have%20frequently%20been%20in%20the%20news%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20Frequent%20incidents%20of%20lynching%2C%20cow%20vigilantism%2C%20attacks%20on%20Muslims%20and%20mosques%2C%20boycott%20campaigns%20against%20public%20offering%20of%20namaz%2C%20and%20hateful%20threats%20on%20social%20media%20against%20the%20Muslim%20community%20by%20Hindutva%20activists%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhow-violent-cow-vigilantism-made-monu-manesar-an-icon%5C%22%3EMonu%20Manesar%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Biitu%20Bajrangi%20have%20kept%20the%20communal%20pot%20boiling%20in%20the%20region.%20This%20has%20resulted%20in%20deep%20mistrust%20between%20communities.%20More%20often%20than%20not%2C%20the%20aggressive%20Hindutva%20activists%20have%20acted%20with%20impunity%2C%20which%20has%20led%20to%20the%20region%20remaining%20constantly%20on%20a%20communal%20boil.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20members%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20of%20Nuh%20said%20that%20the%20violence%20was%20waiting%20to%20happen%20as%20the%20district%20administration%20has%20regularly%20failed%20to%20rein%20in%20%E2%80%9Canti-social%E2%80%9D%20elements%20in%20both%20communities.%20%E2%80%9CWho%20started%20stone-pelting%20isn%E2%80%99t%20clear%20but%20both%20groups%20pelted%20stones%20at%20each%20other%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20Nuh%20resident%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eadding%20that%20frequent%20provocation%20by%20Hindutva%20activists%20has%20precipitated%20such%20a%20situation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20polarisation%20along%20religious%20lines%20is%20evident%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20Monday%20clashes.%20Members%20of%20the%20Hindu%20community%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20mobs%20consisting%20of%20Muslims%20ransacked%20their%20shops%2C%20even%20looted%20liquor%20shops%2C%20and%20set%20many%20cars%20on%20fire.%20As%20per%20locals%2C%20the%20violence%20began%20from%2012%20pm%20and%20continued%20till%208%20in%20the%20evening.%20Police%20failed%20to%20control%20the%20situation%20which%20resulted%20in%20three%20deaths%20on%20Monday.%20Injured%20Bajrang%20Dal%20members%20were%20taken%20to%20the%20neighbouring%20SHKM%20Medical%20College.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20riots%2C%20Nuh%20remained%20tense%20%E2%80%93%20a%20poor%20reflection%20of%20its%20historical%20brotherhood%20between%20faiths.%20Roads%20and%20streets%20mirrored%20the%20arson%20and%20destruction%20that%20Nuh%20witnessed%20on%20Monday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20deputy%20commissioner%20of%20Gurugram%20Nishant%20Kumar%20Yadav%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20that%20a%20sudden%20turn%20of%20events%20on%20Monday%20during%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%9CShobha%20Yatra%E2%80%9D%20escalated%20suddenly.%20Yadav%20said%20that%20misinformation%20circulated%20on%20social%20media%20may%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20communal%20flare-up%20in%20Nuh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20small%20clash%20escalated%20suddenly%20into%20a%20communal%20riot%20owing%20to%20large-scale%20rumour-mongering%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Yatra%20is%20an%20annual%20event.%20The%20district%20administration%20had%20prepared%20adequately.%20There%20was%20a%20peace%20committee%20comprising%20representatives%20from%20both%20faiths%20who%20met%20before%20the%20Yatra.%20We%20had%20deployed%20adequate%20force.%20But%20the%20communal%20build-up%20was%20way%20too%20sudden%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yadav%20said%2C%20responding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20why%20the%20district%20administration%20did%20not%20take%20any%20preemptive%20action%20despite%20a%20widespread%20circulation%20of%20hateful%20videos%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Yatra.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20sudden%20flare-up%20was%20the%20reason%20the%20district%20administration%20could%20not%20deploy%20sufficient%20forces%20on%20time.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01204406%2Fdamaged.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01204406%2Fdamaged.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01204406%2Fdamaged-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01204406%2Fdamaged-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-666161%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERampaging%20groups%20set%20ablaze%20numerous%20vehicles%20amidst%20riots%20in%20Nuh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20district%20police%20has%20already%20filed%20around%2025-30%20FIRs%2C%20and%20that%20the%20situation%20is%20tense%20but%20under%20control%20currently.%20He%20said%20that%2060%20people%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20riots%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fharyana-at-least-1-killed-5-injured-as-clashes-breakout-during-rally-by-hindutva-outfits-in-nuh%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eapart%20from%20the%20three%20who%20were%20killed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20However%2C%20he%20said%20that%20Mohit%20Yadav%20alias%20Monu%20Manesar%20is%20not%20named%20in%20any%20of%20the%20FIRs.%20A%20video%20featuring%20Manesar%20was%20widely%20circulated%20over%20the%20last%20two%20days%20on%20Whatsapp%20in%20which%20he%20is%20seen%20making%20a%20provocative%20appeal%20to%20Hindus%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20Yatra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EManesar%20is%20a%20Bajrang%20Dal%20activist%20who%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Frajasthan-monu-manesar-cow-protection-junaid-nasir%5C%22%3Eprime%20accused%20in%20the%20brutal%20kidnapping%20and%20murder%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20two%20Muslim%20men%2C%20Junaid%20and%20Nasir%2C%20in%20Bhiwani%20early%20this%20year.%20He%20has%20been%20absconding%20since%20then%20but%20had%20released%20a%20video%20claiming%20that%20he%20will%20be%20participating%20in%20the%20Shobha%20Yatra%20on%20Monday.%20His%20social%20media%20accounts%20are%20filled%20with%20videos%20brandishing%20weapons%20and%20provocative%20messaging%20against%20Muslims.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERamzan%20Chowdhary%2C%20who%20is%20a%20member%20of%20a%20peace%20committee%20that%20the%20district%20administration%20had%20formed%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Yatra%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20year%2C%20one%20or%20other%20all%20faiths%20bring%20out%20their%20religious%20processions.%20But%20we%20never%20saw%20communal%20violence.%20In%20fact%2C%20members%20of%20both%20faiths%20have%20seen%20to%20it%20that%20they%20lead%20by%20example%20by%20helping%20each%20other%20in%20organising%20such%20processions.%20However%2C%20social%20media%20videos%2C%20especially%20by%20Monu%20Manesar%20and%20Bittu%20Bajrangi%20who%20are%20seen%20making%20derogatory%20and%20humiliating%20remarks%20about%20the%20Muslims%2C%20led%20to%20severe%20tensions.%20At%20the%20end%2C%20brainless%20and%20foolish%20people%20from%20both%20communities%20clashed%20with%20each%20other.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20is%20why%20I%20had%20informed%20the%20police%20that%20such%20a%20thing%20could%20happen.%20The%20police%20had%20assured%20us%20that%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20let%20Monu%20Manesar%20participate%20in%20the%20Yatra.%20But%20things%20had%20gone%20beyond%20control%20by%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chowdhary%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChowdhary%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20spoken%20about%20possible%20disturbances%20with%20the%20district%20superintendent%20of%20police%20three%20days%20ago.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20last%20year%2C%20one%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emazaars%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(a%20Sufi%20shrine)%20was%20vandalised%2C%20but%20brotherhood%20prevailed%20as%20members%20of%20both%20communities%20prevented%20any%20escalation.%20But%20this%20time%2C%20some%20of%20the%20videos%20were%20really%20venomous%20against%20Muslims.%20In%20one%20of%20the%20videos%2C%20one%20Bittu%20Bajrangi%20said%20that%20Nuh%20was%20the%20Hindu%20community%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esasural%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(in-laws%E2%80%99s%20house)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbout%20which%20community%20started%20pelting%20stones%20is%20unclear%20and%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20investigation%2C%20but%20he%20claimed%20that%20one%20such%20attack%20on%20a%20Muslim%20lawyer%E2%80%99s%20house%20in%20Mevali%20Square%20in%20Nuh%20became%20a%20trigger%20for%20a%20Muslim%20mob.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20denied%20any%20claim%20about%20Hindus%20being%20%E2%80%9Cheld%20hostage%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20temple%20and%20said%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20district%20police%20that%20the%20police%20had%20asked%20people%20caught%20in%20the%20violence%20to%20take%20shelter%20in%20the%20temple%E2%80%99s%20premises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20pre-planned%20attempt%20to%20disturb%20communal%20peace%2C%20and%20trigger%20animosity%20between%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chowdhary%20said.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20locals%20believed%20that%20given%20how%20social%20media%20videos%20were%20being%20circulated%20by%20members%20of%20both%20faiths%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Yatra%2C%20the%20district%20administration%20should%20have%20prevented%20the%20Yatra%20to%20enter%20the%20Muslim-majority%20Nuh.%20Questions%20about%20why%20the%20district%20administration%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20any%20preemptive%20action%20like%20making%20preventive%20arrests%20or%20deploying%20adequate%20police%20personnel%20have%20become%20a%20contested%20topic%20of%20discussion%2C%20as%20polarising%20sentiments%20appear%20to%20be%20getting%20a%20free%20run%20at%20the%20moment.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690902432000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01204256%2FTemple.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnuh-temple-priest-refutes-haryana-home-ministers-claim-that-people-are-held-hostage%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20communal%20clashes%20broke%20out%20in%20Nuh%20on%20Monday%2C%20Anil%20Vij%20claimed%20that%20around%203%2C000%20to%204%2C000%20people%20were%20'held%20hostage'%20by%20Muslim%20rioters%20at%20the%20Nalhar%20Mahadev%20temple.%20The%20Wire%20brings%20a%20ground%20report%20from%20the%20violence-hit%20areas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnuh-temple-priest-refutes-haryana-home-ministers-claim-that-people-are-held-hostage%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine%20says%20doctor%20killed%20in%20Russian%20shelling%20of%20Kherson%20hospital%22%2C%