uality%20and%20justice%2C%20while%20its%20opponents%20fear%20that%20it%20may%20lead%20to%20the%20erosion%20of%20minority%20rights%20and%20cultural%20diversity.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStriking%20an%20equilibrium%20between%20Articles%2025-28%20and%20Article%2044%20of%20the%20constitution%20while%20implementing%20the%20UCC%20is%20of%20utmost%20importance%20to%20ensure%20that%20this%20process%20is%20not%20just%20a%20political%20ploy%2C%20but%20the%20intellectually%20deliberated%20pursuit%20of%20harmonious%20governance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20need%20for%20a%20UCC%20must%20not%20be%20driven%20by%20emotional%20arguments%20of%20either%20the%20majority%20or%20minority%20communities%2C%20nor%20should%20it%20be%20a%20political%20charade.%20Instead%2C%20it%20must%20be%20approached%20with%20intellectual%20labour%20and%20rigorous%20deliberations%2C%20considering%20its%20implications%20on%20the%20diverse%20fabric%20of%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EArticle%2044%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20which%20promotes%20the%20UCC%2C%20is%20a%20Directive%20Principle%20of%20State%20Policy%20(DPSP).%20These%20principles%20are%20guidelines%20for%20the%20government%20to%20achieve%20social%20and%20economic%20democracy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20UCC%2C%20as%20a%20DPSP%2C%20calls%20for%20taking%20into%20account%20the%20evolving%20nature%20of%20the%20country%20and%20its%20society.%20Any%20effort%20to%20implement%20the%20UCC%20should%20seek%20to%20preserve%20and%20respect%20the%20unique%20cultural%20identities%20of%20various%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20current%20political%20move%20found%20support%20in%20the%20judgement%20by%20Justices%20Kuldip%20Singh%20and%20R.M.%20Sahai%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F733037%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESarla%20Mudgal%20vs%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(1995).%20In%20this%20landmark%20case%2C%20the%20judgement%C2%A0raised%20the%20question%20of%20a%20common%20civil%20code%20and%20its%20potential%20implications%20for%20the%20freedom%20of%20religion%20guaranteed%20by%20the%20constitution.%20The%20case%20remains%20a%20pivotal%20reference%20in%20the%20ongoing%20discourse%20about%20a%20UCC.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-knows-an-actual-ucc-will-be-an-electoral-disaster-for-him%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%20Knows%20an%20Actual%20UCC%20Will%20Be%20an%20Electoral%20Disaster%20for%20Him%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESarla%20Mudgal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20emphasises%20the%20need%20for%20a%20UCC%20as%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20issue%20raised%20in%20the%20case%2C%20holding%20that%20the%20second%20marriage%20of%20a%20Hindu%20husband%20after%20conversion%20to%20Islam%2C%20without%20dissolving%20his%20first%20marriage%20under%20law%2C%20to%20be%20invalid.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20court%2C%20emphasising%20on%20misuse%20of%20personal%20laws%2C%20reiterates%20that%20Article%2044%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20mandates%20the%20state%20to%20secure%20a%20UCC%20for%20all%20its%20citizens.%20A%20well-implemented%20UCC%20can%20rectify%20such%20discrepancies%20and%20ensure%20gender%20justice%20and%20equal%20rights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJustice%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20observation%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESarla%20Mudgal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20highlights%20that%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20UCC%2C%20individuals%20might%20attempt%20to%20misuse%20religious%20freedoms%20to%20evade%20legal%20restrictions.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Sahai%20also%20opined%20that%20practices%20associated%20with%20different%20religions%20may%20appear%20excessive%20or%20conflicting%20to%20others%2C%20but%20they%20are%20matters%20of%20conscience%20and%20should%20be%20approached%20with%20respect.%20Reason%20and%20logic%20may%20not%20play%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20such%20matters%3B%20instead%2C%20emotions%20need%20to%20be%20tempered%20with%20sincere%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20need%20for%20a%20UCC%20is%20acknowledged%2C%20but%20its%20successful%20implementation%20requires%20the%20cooperation%20of%20enlightened%20individuals%2C%20statesmen%20and%20leaders%20who%20can%20create%20a%20conducive%20social%20climate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETheir%20stance%2C%20however%2C%20was%20strongly%20criticised%20by%20the%20distinguished%20constitutional%20lawyer%20H.M.%20Seervai%2C%20in%20an%20article%20titled%20%E2%80%98Uniform%20Civil%20Code%3A%20Judiciary%20Oversteps%20its%20Brief%E2%80%99%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3B%20July%205%2C%201995).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20article%20highlighted%20that%20the%20judges%20had%20ventured%20beyond%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20case%20and%20addressed%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20common%20civil%20code.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJustice%20Kuldip%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20argument%2C%20linking%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20UCC%20to%20Hindu%20men%20converting%20to%20Islam%20to%20marry%20multiple%20wives%2C%20was%20deemed%20specious.%20Justice%20Sahai%20dissented%20and%20emphasised%20that%20religion%20encompasses%20more%20than%20just%20faith%20and%20belief.%20The%20judges%20overlooked%20Article%20145(5)%2C%20requiring%20majority%20concurrence%2C%20rendering%20their%20opinion%20on%20the%20compatibility%20of%20a%20UCC%20with%20freedom%20of%20religion%20inconclusive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeervai%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20judiciary%20cannot%20enforce%20Article%2044%2C%20which%20calls%20for%20a%20UCC%2C%20as%20it%20falls%20under%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20executive%20and%20parliament.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20core%20principles%20behind%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20UCC%20is%20to%20ensure%20gender%20justice%20and%20equal%20rights.%20A%20well-crafted%20code%20should%20address%20discriminatory%20practices%20in%20personal%20laws%20and%20promote%20a%20more%20equitable%20society.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20UCC%20must%20not%20be%20used%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20impose%20majority%20beliefs%20on%20minority%20communities%2C%20or%20to%20attack%20their%20cultural%20practices.%20A%20balanced%20approach%20that%20respects%20diversity%20and%20protects%20minority%20rights%20is%20crucial.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUpon%20examining%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20debates%2C%20it%20is%20evident%20that%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20believed%20in%20the%20significance%20of%20a%20UCC.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2FDr._Babasaheb_Ambedkar_chairman_of_the_Drafting_Committee_presenting_the_final_draft_of_the_Indian_Constitution_to_Dr._Rajendra_Prasad_on_25_November_1949.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22670%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-204340%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22526%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20(L)%20after%20presenting%20the%20constitution%20to%20the%20first%20president%20Dr%20Rajendra%20Prasad%20(R).%20Credit%3A%20Unknown%20author%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20Public%20domain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20considering%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%2C%20his%20stance%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20individual%20choice%20in%20matters%20of%20marriage%20aligns%20with%20the%20principles%20reflected%20in%20the%20Act.%20Ambedkar%20emphasised%20that%20a%20UCC%20should%20be%20implemented%20voluntarily%2C%20considering%20the%20sentiments%20and%20preferences%20of%20various%20religious%20communities%20in%20order%20to%20foster%20a%20harmonious%20evolution%20of%20a%20uniform%20civil%20law.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20inclusion%20of%20the%20UCC%20in%20the%20DPSP%20should%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20guiding%20principle%20for%20formulating%20laws%20and%20policies%2C%20rather%20than%20a%20strict%20mandate.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20current%20debates%20surrounding%20the%20UCC%20are%20often%20politically%20motivated.%20Instead%20of%20engaging%20in%20mere%20rhetoric%2C%20policymakers%20must%20focus%20on%20drafting%20a%20comprehensive%20law%20that%20considers%20the%20diverse%20religious%20freedoms%20and%20practices%20while%20ensuring%20constitutional%20objectives%20are%20met.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20quest%20for%20equilibrium%20between%20Articles%2025-28%20and%20Article%2044%20while%20implementing%20the%20uniform%20civil%20code%20is%20a%20multifaceted%20challenge.%20It%20requires%20intellectual%20rigour%2C%20unbiased%20deliberations%20and%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20diversity%20and%20cultural%20fabric.%20A%20well-crafted%20UCC%20can%20foster%20gender%20justice%2C%20equal%20rights%20and%20social%20harmony%2C%20without%20compromising%20the%20essence%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20unity%20in%20diversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStriking%20this%20balance%20is%20essential%20for%20building%20a%20progressive%2C%20inclusive%20and%20just%20society%20for%20all%20citizens.%20Also%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20recognise%20the%20significant%20value%20of%20Article%2025-28%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20which%20enshrines%20the%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20religion%20as%20a%20fundamental%20right.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20expectation%20from%20the%2022nd%20Law%20Commission%20is%20that%20it%20will%20adopt%20an%20impartial%2C%20consultative%20and%20attentive%20approach%20in%20understanding%20the%20complexities%20surrounding%20the%20uniform%20civil%20code%2C%20and%20consider%20the%20viewpoints%20of%20all%20relevant%20stakeholders%20before%20formulating%20any%20recommendations%20or%20proposals%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAravindan%20Anandan%20is%20assistant%20professor%2C%20School%20of%20Legal%20Studies%20and%20Governance%2C%20Vidyashilp%20University%2C%20Bengaluru%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690891256000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01170315%2FSeesaw-but-in-a-void.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fequilibrium-between-religious-freedom-and-ucc-dpsp%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Striking%20a%20balance%20between%20equality%20and%20religious%20freedom%20requires%20unbiased%20deliberation%20and%20intellectual%20rigour%2C%20but%20the%20current%20debates%20surrounding%20the%20UCC%20are%20often%20politically%20motivated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fequilibrium-between-religious-freedom-and-ucc-dpsp%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Incapable%20or%20Uninterested'%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Tears%20Into%20Manipur%20Police%20Over%20Handling%20of%20Violence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20taken%20a%20dim%20view%20of%20law%20enforcement%20and%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20handling%20of%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20calling%20police%20investigation%20%E2%80%9Ctardy%E2%80%9D%20and%20asking%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20to%20be%20present%20in%20court%20on%20August%204%20to%20be%20able%20to%20answer%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-manipur-violence-absolute-breakdown-of-machinery-of-state-in-manipur-no-law-order-summons-dgp-234099%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%2C%20Justice%20JB%20Pardiwala%20and%20Justice%20Manoj%20Misra%2C%20who%20are%20hearing%20a%20bunch%20of%20petitions%20on%20the%20Manipur%20violence%2C%20including%20those%20by%20victims%20of%20sexual%20violence%2C%20was%20%E2%80%9Caghast%E2%80%9D%20to%20learn%20that%20FIRs%20have%20not%20been%20registered%20for%20nearly%20three%20months%20after%20some%20occurrences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20learned%20that%20only%20a%20few%20arrests%20had%20been%20made%20in%20the%206%2C000%20FIRs%20that%20have%20been%20registered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBased%20on%20the%20preliminary%20data%2C%20it%20does%20prima%20facie%20appear%20that%20the%20investigation%20has%20been%20tardy.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20considerable%20lapse%20between%20the%20occurrence%20and%20the%20registration%20of%20FIRs%2C%20recording%20of%20witness%20statements%20and%20even%20the%20arrests%20are%20few%20and%20far%20between.%20In%20order%20to%20enable%20the%20court%20to%20appreciate%20the%20entire%20dimensions%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20investigation%20that%20is%20required%2C%20we%20direct%20the%20DGP%20of%20Manipur%20to%20be%20personally%20present%20in%20the%20Court%20at%20Friday%202%20PM%20and%20be%20in%20a%20position%20of%20answer%20the%20queries%20of%20the%20Court%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20apex%20court%20observed%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20of%20India%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20appearing%20for%20Manipur%2C%20said%20he%20was%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20give%20details%20on%20how%20many%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9C6%2C532%20FIRs%E2%80%9D%20filed%20were%20%E2%80%9Czero%20FIRs%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESG%20Mehta%20also%20could%20not%20answer%20when%20the%20arrests%20in%20the%20case%20relating%20to%20the%20sexual%20violence%20video%20took%20place.%20As%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-video-arrest-biren-singh-supreme-court%5C%22%3Efirst%20arrest%20was%20announced%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20July%2020%2C%20after%20the%20video%20went%20viral%20and%20sparked%20nationwide%20outrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20appears%20to%20be%2C%20subject%20to%20correction%2C%20after%20the%20video%20surfaced%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20SG%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20said%20that%20one%20thing%20was%20very%20clear%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20is%20such%20a%20long%20delay%20in%20filing%20FIRs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20also%20observed%20that%20few%20arrests%20have%20taken%20place%20with%20the%20exception%20of%20one%20of%20two%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInvestigation%20is%20so%20lethargic.%20FIRs%20registered%20after%20two%20months.%20Arrests%20not%20made.%20Statements%20recorded%20after%20a%20long%20lapse%20of%20time%E2%80%9D%2C%20CJI%20added%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20also%20said%20that%20this%20gives%20the%20judges%20the%20impression%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20was%20%5Bsuch%20an%5D%20absolute%20breakdown%20of%20machinery%20that%20you%20could%20not%20even%20register%20FIR.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CState%20police%20is%20incapable%20of%20investigation.%20They%20have%20lost%20control.%20There%20is%20absolutely%20no%20law%20and%20order%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CJI%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20exclaimed%20that%20only%20seven%20arrests%20had%20been%20made%20out%20of%206%2C000%20FIRs%2C%20SG%20Mehta%20sought%20to%20clarify%20that%20these%20were%20made%20in%20respect%20of%20the%20viral%20video%20case%20and%20250%20arrests%20were%20made%20in%20total.%20SG%20Mehta%20said%20%E2%80%9C12000%E2%80%9D%20preventive%20arrests%20have%20been%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20also%2C%20crucially%2C%20asked%20if%20policemen%20had%20been%20interrogated%20after%20women%20said%20that%20cops%20had%20handed%20them%20over%20to%20the%20mob.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20the%20DGP%20doing%3F%20It%20is%20his%20duty%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CJI%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20called%20the%20arrests%20made%20%E2%80%9Cperformative.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEither%20they%20were%20incapable%20of%20doing%20it%20or%20uninterested%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CJI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20ago%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwe-cant-justify-what-happened-in-manipur-by-saying-this-happened-elsewhere-sc%5C%22%3Enoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20cannot%20justify%20what%20happened%20in%20Manipur%20by%20saying%20that%20this%20and%20this%20happened%20elsewhere.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690890802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-manipur-violence-police%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20bench%2C%20crucially%2C%20asked%20if%20policemen%20had%20been%20interrogated%20after%20women%20said%20that%20cops%20had%20handed%20them%20over%20to%20the%20mob.%20'What%20is%20the%20DGP%20doing%3F'%20is%20asked.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A91%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-manipur-violence-police%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20limits%20drone%20exports%20as%20Russia%20compares%20Moscow%20strike%20to%209%2F11%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690889640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F768x432%2Fskynews-moscow-russia-drone-attack_6236693.jpg%3F20230801073032%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fchina-limits-drone-exports-over-fears-they-are-being-used-in-ukraine-conflict-12931690%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%20is%20to%20limit%20the%20export%20of%20long-range%20drones%20over%20fears%20they%20are%20being%20converted%20for%20military%20use%20in%20Ukraine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A270%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fchina-limits-drone-exports-over-fears-they-are-being-used-in-ukraine-conflict-12931690%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fchina-limits-drone-exports-over-fears-they-are-being-used-in-ukraine-conflict-12931690%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fchina-limits-drone-exports-over-fears-they-are-being-used-in-ukraine-conflict-12931690%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Justice%20Rohini%20Panel%20Submits%20Report%2C%20Will%20the%20Modi%20Govt%20Move%20Ahead%20with%20Sub-Quotas%20for%20OBCs%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F22141813%2Fnalsar-final.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ESix%20years%20after%20it%20was%20constituted%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpanel-for-obc-sub-categorisation-gets-its-14th-extension%5C%22%3Efollowing%2014%20extensions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Rohini%20Commission%2C%20tasked%20with%20the%20sub-categorisation%20of%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%2C%20submitted%20its%20report%20to%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20on%20Monday%2C%20July%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20commission%20report%20submitted%2C%20the%20ball%20is%20now%20in%20the%20court%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20on%20whether%20or%20not%20it%20would%20want%20to%20apportion%20the%20existing%2027%25%20reservation%20among%20various%20groups%20which%20are%20part%20of%20the%20OBCs.%20The%20Commission%20was%20constituted%20in%20October%202017%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20amid%20expectations%20that%20it%20would%20lead%20to%20the%20sub-division%20of%20the%20reservation%20pool%20among%20OBC%20communities%20depending%20upon%20the%20population%20and%20deprivation%20of%20particular%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20complaint%20among%20relatively%20backward%20communities%20among%20OBCs%20that%20those%20OBC%20groups%20with%20relatively%20good%20economic%20standing%20and%20educational%20standards%20have%20been%20grabbing%20the%20benefits%20of%20reservations%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20most%20deprived%20communities.%20The%20sub-grouping%2C%20many%20believe%2C%20would%20lead%20to%20equitable%20distribution%20of%20reservation%20benefits%20among%20the%20constituent%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20Commission%20was%20to%20submit%20its%20report%20in%2012%20weeks%2C%20following%20its%20constitution%20in%20October%202017%2C%20it%20has%20been%20given%2014%20extensions%20and%20its%20tenure%20finally%20ended%20on%20Monday%2C%20July%2031.%20It%20is%20widely%20believed%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20following%20the%20constitution%20of%20the%20commission%2C%20had%20a%20rethink%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20for%20such%20a%20move%20to%20divide%20the%20reservation%20pool%20among%20OBCs%20could%20trigger%20controversy%20and%20affect%20its%20political%20fortunes.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20dragged%20its%20feet%20on%20the%20issue%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20Rohini%20Commission%20has%20submitted%20its%20report%20at%20a%20time%20when%20there%20is%20a%20growing%20clamour%20from%20the%20opposition%20parties%20to%20conduct%20a%20nationwide%20census%20assumes%20significance.%20The%20BJP%20has%20been%20opposed%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20caste%20census.%20In%20fact%2C%20Mandalite%20parties%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%2C%20have%20said%20if%20the%20government%20intends%20to%20go%20for%20division%20of%20the%20reservation%20pool%20among%20the%20OBCs%2C%20it%20should%20first%20carry%20out%20caste%20census%20to%20obtain%20information%20on%20the%20population%20share%20of%20constituent%20groups%20among%20the%20OBCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20government%20notification%2C%20the%20commission%20headed%20by%20retired%20Justice%20G.%20Rohini%20of%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20was%20also%20tasked%20with%20recommending%20the%20correction%20of%20any%20repetitions%2C%20ambiguities%2C%20inconsistencies%2C%20and%20errors%20of%20spelling%20or%20transcription%2C%20examining%20the%20extent%20of%20inequitable%20distribution%20of%20benefits%20of%20reservation%20among%20the%20OBCs%2C%20and%20working%20out%20the%20mechanism%2C%20criteria%2C%20norms%20and%20parameters%20in%20a%20scientific%20approach%2C%20for%20sub-categorisation%20within%20such%20OBCs%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Frohini-commission-examining-sub-categorisation-obc-report-president-8870799%2F%5C%22%3EPTI%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690889438000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F22141813%2Fnalsar-final.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fas-justice-rohini-panel-submits-report-will-the-modi-govt-move-ahead-with-sub-quotas-for-obcs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Commission%20formed%20in%20October%202017%20was%20tasked%20with%20examining%20the%20extent%20of%20inequitable%20distribution%20of%20benefits%20of%20reservation%20among%20the%20OBCs.%20It%20finally%20submitted%20its%20report%20on%20Monday%2C%20after%2014%20extensions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fas-justice-rohini-panel-submits-report-will-the-modi-govt-move-ahead-with-sub-quotas-for-obcs%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22British%20man%20who%20killed%20terminally%20ill%20wife%20visits%20her%20grave%20for%20first%20time%20after%20prison%20release%22%2C%22content%22