m%20Policy%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERai%20also%20spoke%20of%20the%20existence%20of%20a%20committee%20named%20%E2%80%98One%20Nation%20One%20Police%20Uniform.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20reply%20to%20a%20question%20raised%20by%20six%20MPs%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Rai%20said%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20Chintan%20Shivir%20of%20Home%20Ministers%20of%20States%20organised%20by%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20on%2027-28th%20October%202022%2C%20it%20was%20suggested%20to%20the%20States%20to%20consider%20the%20One%20Nation%20One%20Police%20Uniform%20to%20create%20a%20distinct%20identity%20of%20police%20and%20to%20ensure%20that%20citizens%20easily%20recognize%20police%20personnel%20across%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20six%20MPs%20who%20asked%20the%20question%20are%20from%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20breakaway%20faction%20of%20Eknath%20Shinde.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20government%20said%20that%2024%20states%20have%20responded%20to%20the%20government%20on%20this%20and%20a%20committee%20has%20been%20constituted%20in%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Police%20Research%20%26amp%3B%20Development.%20This%20committee%20has%20some%20members%20of%20states%20and%20Union%20territories%2C%20representatives%20of%20Textile%20Research%20Associations%2C%20the%20Troop%20Comforts%20Limited%20and%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Indian%20Standard%20(BIS).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPolice%20and%20law%20and%20order%20is%20a%20state%20subject%20in%20the%20state%20list%20of%20the%20Seventh%20Schedule.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20clarity%20yet%20on%20what%20the%2024%20states%20have%20said%20in%20response.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPolice%20reform%20has%20been%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%20for%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20as%20well%20as%20activists.%20Conditions%20in%