The%20excess%20farm%20produce%20is%20converted%20into%20useful%20products%20like%20dry%20powder%2C%20flakes%2C%20and%20toppings.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20two%20types%20of%20designs%20%E2%80%94%20the%20first%20is%20foldable%20and%20portable%2C%20and%20the%20other%20is%20a%20fixed%20polyhouse%20design.%20We%20have%20designed%20foldable%20ones%2C%20especially%20for%20small%20and%20marginal%20farmers.%20These%20are%2040%20feet%20long%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F90357%2Fs4s-solar-dryer-vaibhav-tidke%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20dryers%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20can%20be%20folded%20into%20a%20five-foot%20box.%20This%20helps%20us%20install%20them%20in%20remote%20locations%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Varun%2C%20who%20has%20priced%20a%2020%20kg%20solar%20dryer%20at%20Rs%2024%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20half%20the%20price%20of%20those%20available%20in%20the%20market.%20Starting%20from%20five%20kg%2C%20he%20has%20solar%20dryers%20up%20to%20a%20capacity%20of%201%2C000%20kg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20he%20has%20installed%20over%203%2C500%20solar%20dryers%20in%20the%20rural%20and%20remote%20farms%20of%20the%20country%20including%20Kashmir%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Manipur%2C%20Arunachal%20and%20Gujarat.%20Every%20month%2C%20the%20farmers%20are%20able%20to%20monthly%20process%20115%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20fresh%20produce%2C%20which%20would%20otherwise%20go%20to%20waste%2C%20into%20useful%20products%20like%20dry%20powder%2C%20flakes%2C%20and%20toppings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20reached%20out%20to%20farmers%20in%20remote%20areas%20where%20they%20cannot%20access%20the%20market%20easily.%20For%20example%2C%20pineapples%20grown%20in%20Manipur%20are%20sold%20at%20Rs%20250%20per%20piece%20in%20markets%20like%20Delhi%20and%20Mumbai.%20But%20locally%2C%20they%20have%20a%20value%20of%20Rs%205.%20Still%2C%20a%20bu