ia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faadya-bennur-1-1690377934-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faadya-bennur-1-1690377934-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faadya-bennur-1-1690377934-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faadya-bennur-1-1690377934-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325231%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAadya%20followed%20a%20strict%20exercise%20regime%20before%20going%20on%20the%20expedition%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Harsha%20Bennur%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F295904%2Ftravelling-elderly-couple-climb-mount-kilimanjaro-create-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClimbing%20Kilimanjaro%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20very%20difficult.%20The%20weather%20was%20extremely%20cold%2C%20and%20the%20food%20was%20very%20bad!%20It%20was%20taking%20me%20longer%20to%20eat%20it%20as%20it%20did%20not%20taste%20as%20good%20as%20my%20mother%E2%80%99s%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CI%20missed%20my%20mother%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20I%20was%20determined%20to%20keep%20going.%20I%20kept%20picturing%20how%20stunning%20the%20peak%20would%20be%20and%20looked%20forward%20to%20a%20big%20party%20at%20home%20once%20I%20returned.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20an%20average%20adult%2C%20it%20takes%20about%20seven%20to%20nine%20days%20to%20reach%20Mount%20Kilimanjaro%E2%80%99s%20summit%20and%20then%20descend%20to%20the%20finishing%20point.%20The%20trek%20is%20a%2064-km%20hike%20with%20the%20peak%20standing%20at%2019%2C340%20feet%20above%20sea%20level.%20Considered%20to%20be%20a%20moderately%20difficult%20climb%2C%20its%20low%20oxygen%20environment%20and%20low%20temperatures%20are%20both%20physically%20and%2