20locations%20beforehand%2C%20along%20with%20their%20families%2C%20before%20planning%20it%20for%20others.%20They%20mostly%20book%20homestays%20or%20boutique%20hotels%20with%20kitchenettes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trips%20are%20usually%20priced%20around%20Rs%2020%2C000%E2%80%93Rs%2025%2C000%2C%20and%20each%20mother%20is%20given%20a%20separate%20room%20with%20her%20child%2Fchildren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20816px)%20100vw%2C%20816px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel3-1690375408.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22816%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22travel%20with%20kids%20india%20takes%20mothers%20and%20children%20on%20trips%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel3-1690375408.jpg%20816w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel3-1690375408-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel3-1690375408-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel3-1690375408-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel3-1690375408-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel3-1690375408-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325208%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22816%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChildren%20are%20usually%20between%20the%20age%20group%20of%202-12.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20we%20form%20a%20WhatsApp%20group%20after%20people%20book%20the%20trip.%20We%20interact%20initially%20to%20understand%20the%20needs%20and%20eating%20habits%20of%20the%20moms%20and%20children%2C%20accommodating%20any%20special%20requirements%20through%20a%20detailed%20form.%20We%20also%20arrange%20Zoom%20calls%20for%20the%20moms%20t