0Moy%20Moy%2C%20this%20great%2C%20funny%2C%20little%20child.%20But%20when%20she%20started%20going%20to%20school%2C%20it%20was%20as%20if%20they%20put%20a%20spotlight%20on%20her%20difficulties.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20we%20realised%20this%20school%20system%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20right%20for%20Moy%20Moy.%20Everything%20at%20the%20Foundation%20has%20evolved%20from%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20put%20in%20place%20many%20provisions%20in%20the%20form%20of%20laws%20and%20policies%20for%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%20but%20the%20implementation%20remains%20questionable.%20%3Cem%3EOutlook%20India%20%3C%2Fem%3Enoted%20of%20all%20the%20children%20with%20disabilities%20in%20India%2C%20three-fourths%20of%20those%20aged%20aged%20five%20don%E2%80%99t%20attend%20any%20educational%20institution.%20About%2012%25%20drop%20out%2C%20and%2027%25%20have%20never%20attended%20any%20educational%20institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20UNICEF%20report%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20early%20years%20(0%20to%208%20years)%20are%20the%20most%20extraordinary%20period%20of%20growth%20and%20development%20in%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20lifetime.%20The%20foundations%20of%20all%20learning%20are%20laid%20during%20these%20years.%20Getting%20the%20foundations%20right%20carries%20huge%20future%20benefits%3A%20better%20learning%20in%20school%20and%20higher%20educational%20attainment%2C%20which%20results%20in%20major%20social%20and%20economic%20gains%20for%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20820px)%20100vw%2C%20820px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Finclusive-education-1690291697.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22820%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22inclusive%20education%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Finclusive-education-1690291697.jpg%20820w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%